%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Meta%20is%20suing%20a%20former%20exec%20it%20claims%20took%20a%20trove%20of%20'highly%20sensitive'%20documents%20just%20before%20joining%20an%20AI%20startup%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%20this%20photo%20illustration%2C%20a%20Meta%20logo%20is%20displayed%20on%20a%20smartphone%20with%20stock%20market%20percentages%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65633126fe5bc6545ebc06ff%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223327%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMeta%20is%20suing%20a%20former%20employee%20who%20joined%20an%20AI%20startup.%20%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMeta%20is%20suing%20a%20former%20VP%20following%20his%20decision%20to%20join%20an%20AI%20startup.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20lawsuit%20claims%20the%20former%20worker%20took%20sensitive%20documents%20about%20Meta's%20business%20and%20employees.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMeta%20claims%20that%20eight%20employees%20listed%20in%20the%20documents%20have%20joined%20the%20same%20AI%20startup.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMeta%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20suing%20a%20former%20executive%20over%20his%20defection%20to%20an%20AI%20startup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20lawsuit%20first%20reported%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2024-03-12%2Fmeta-sues-disloyal-former-vp-over-alleged-stolen-documents%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Meta%20accused%20Dipinder%20Singh%20Khurana%20of%20taking%20private%20documents%20with%20him%20when%20he%20left%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20suit%20alleges%20Khurana%2C%20a%20former%20vice-president%20of%20infrastructure%2C%20violated%20his%20contract%20by%20taking%20a%20%26quot%3Btrove%20of%20proprietary%2C%20highly%20sensitive%2C%20confidential%2C%20and%20non-public%20documents%20about%20Meta's%20business%20and%20employees.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20called%20the%20move%20a%20%26quot%3Bstunning%26quot%3B%20betrayal%20and%20accused%20Khurana%20of%20being%20%26quot%3Bbrazenly%20disloyal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20claimed%20Khurana%20uploaded%20internal%20documents%2C%20including%20the%20company's%20%26quot%3BTop%20Talent%26quot%3B%20dossier%2C%20to%20his%20personal%20Google%20Drive%20and%20Dropbox%20just%20before%20departing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTaken%20together%2C%20the%20sensitive%2C%20confidential%2C%20and%20non-public%20information%20in%20these%20spreadsheets%20provides%20an%20inside%20view%20as%20to%20how%20Meta%20makes%20compensation%20decisions%20and%20also%20provides%20key%20information%20regarding%20not%20just%20the%20names%20of%20Meta%20employees%20but%20their%20levels%2C%20performance%2C%20and%20skills%20at%20Meta%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20complaint%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Information%20reported%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D2f90dd75eda6073893cd282b822abec979d55ec6a6c1b82dd00d9cb8856f8569%26postID%3D65f1829248eec3d3e787f9c0%26postSlug%3Dmeta-suing-exec-claims-took-trove-sensitive-documents-joined-startup-2024-3%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.theinformation.com%252Farticles%252Fai-agenda-the-mysterious-ai-data-center-startup-hiring-from-aws-azure-meta%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKhurana%20now%20works%20for%20Omniva%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20company%20operating%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20that%20aims%20to%20lower%20the%3Cbr%3Ecost%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%20computing.%20In%20the%20suit%2C%20Meta%20claimed%20that%20eight%20employees%20listed%20in%20the%20documents%20also%20left%20to%20join%20the%20AI%20startup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20it%20%26quot%3Btakes%20this%20kind%20of%20egregious%20misconduct%20seriously.%20We%20will%20continue%20working%20to%20protect%20confidential%20business%20and%20employee%20information.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKhurana%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20BI%20made%20via%20LinkedIn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-suing-exec-claims-took-trove-sensitive-documents-joined-startup-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710415542000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65f18f1b90413ab8e1dc030a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-suing-exec-claims-took-trove-sensitive-documents-joined-startup-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Meta's%20lawsuit%20accuses%20the%20former%20VP%20of%20being%20%26quot%3Bbrazenly%20disloyal%26quot%3B%20by%20uploading%20internal%20documents%20to%20his%20personal%20drive%20just%20before%20leaving.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bnolan%40insider.com%20(Beatrice%20Nolan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-suing-exec-claims-took-trove-sensitive-documents-joined-startup-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I'm%20a%20financial%20planner%20with%206%20overlooked%20tax%20credits%20you%20could%20be%20missing%20out%20on%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20offers%20and%20details%20on%20this%20page%20may%20have%20updated%20or%20changed%20since%20the%20time%20of%20publication.%20See%20our%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffinancial-planner-overlooked-tax-credits-deductions-you-should-know-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20current%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20experts%20answer%20readers'%20tax%20questions%20and%20write%20unbiased%20product%20reviews%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Ftax-review-board-experts%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere's%20how%20we%20assess%20tax%20products%3C%2Fa%3E).%20In%20some%20cases%2C%20we%20receive%20a%20commission%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Four-partners%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eour%20partners%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20however%2C%20our%20opinions%20are%20our%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22hanna%20horvath%20headshot%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65f206176080194819ff8f7d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%2C%20Hanna%20Horvath.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20Hanna%20Horvath%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EYou've%20probably%20already%20thought%20about%20some%20tax%20deductions%2C%20but%20you%20might%20be%20missing%20some%20savings.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIf%20you%20made%20energy-efficient%20updates%20to%20your%20home%2C%20there%20are%20federal%20and%20state%20credits%20and%20deductions.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIf%20you%20paid%20interest%20on%20your%20student%20loans%2C%20you%20can%20deduct%20that%20amount%20at%20tax%20time.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Ftaxes%5C%22%3Etax%20season%3C%2Fa%3E%20again.%20As%20you%20gather%20your%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fwhat-is-w-2-form%5C%22%3EW-2s%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20prepare%20your%20return%2C%20your%20mind%20is%20likely%20focused%20on%20big-ticket%20items%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-mortgage-lenders%5C%22%3Emortgage%3C%2Fa%3E%20interest%2C%20charitable%20donations%2C%20and%20childcare%20costs%20that%20can%20substantially%20lower%20your%20tax%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20some%20smaller%2C%20more%20specialized%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Ftax-credit-vs-tax-deduction%5C%22%3Etax%20credits%20and%20deductions%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%20score%20you%20hundreds%20(or%20even%20thousands)%20of%20extra%20dollars%20back%20as%20well.%20These%20%26quot%3Bhidden%20gems%26quot%3B%20can%20be%20especially%20valuable%20depending%20on%20your%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20an%20overview%20of%20some%20overlooked%20federal%20and%20state%20tax%20credits%20that%20filers%20often%20miss.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E1.%20Green%20credits%20for%20energy%20efficiency%20and%20electric%20vehicles%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20help%20promote%20sustainability%20and%20fight%20climate%20change%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fcleanenergy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20federal%20government%3C%2Fa%3E%20offers%20several%20tax%20incentives%20for%20households%20and%20drivers%20investing%20in%20energy-efficient%20upgrades%20or%20electric%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHome%20upgrades%20like%20installing%20high-efficiency%20HVAC%20systems%2C%20water%20heaters%2C%20solar%20panels%2C%20wind%20turbines%2C%20insulation%2C%20and%20more%20can%20qualify%20for%20credits%20that%20reduce%20what%20you%20owe%20on%20your%20taxes.%20The%20amounts%20and%20specifications%20differ%20based%20on%20the%20type%20of%20upgrade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20purchasers%20of%20electric%20vehicles%20or%20plug-in%20hybrids%20may%20be%20eligible%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.irs.gov%2Fcredits-deductions%2Fcredits-for-new-clean-vehicles-purchased-in-2023-or-after%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecredits%20of%20up%20to%20%247%2C500%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20car's%20battery%20capacity.%20It's%20important%20to%20note%20that%20these%20are%20tax%20credits%2C%20not%20deductions%2C%20meaning%20they%20directly%20reduce%20taxes%20owed%20instead%20of%20just%20reducing%20your%20taxable%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20states%20also%20supplement%20federal%20credits%20with%20additional%20rebates%2C%20discounts%2C%20or%20incentives%20for%20energy-efficient%20products%20and%20electric%20vehicles%20%E2%80%94%20and%20some%20are%20quite%20generous.%20For%20example%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.energysage.com%2Flocal-data%2Fstorage-rebates-incentives%2Fca%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECalifornia%20offers%20thousands%3C%2Fa%3E%20back%20on%20solar%20panels%20and%20electric%20cars%20through%20state%20agencies.%20Before%20investing%20in%20any%20major%20energy%20or%20auto%20upgrade%2C%20review%20the%20available%20federal%20tax%20credits%20and%20state%20incentives%20to%20ensure%20you're%20eligible.%20Combined%2C%20these%20can%20potentially%20add%20up%20to%20major%20savings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E2.%20Health%20insurance%20premium%20deduction%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fself-employed-tax-deductions%5C%22%3EIf%20you're%20a%20freelancer%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20you%20can%20deduct%20your%20health%20insurance%20premiums.%20This%20can%20be%20a%20huge%20deduction%20for%20self-employed%20individuals%20and%20small%20business%20owners%20who%20have%20to%20pay%20for%20health%20insurance%20on%20their%20own.%20Many%20freelancers%20choose%20to%20go%20without%20insurance%20due%20to%20the%20cost%20%E2%80%94%20knowing%20about%20this%20deduction%20can%20help%20lessen%20the%20financial%20blow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20employed%20workers%20have%20employer-sponsored%20health%20insurance%20contributions%20taken%20from%20their%20paycheck%20pre-tax%20%E2%80%94%20and%20those%20paying%20for%20their%20own%20plans%20do%20not.%20This%20levels%20the%20playing%20field%20a%20bit%20for%20the%20self-employed%20by%20making%20health%20insurance%20premiums%20pre-tax.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E3.%20Student%20loan%20interest%20deduction%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20better%20or%20worse%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-private-student-loans%5C%22%3Estudent%20loans%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20become%20synonymous%20with%20higher%20education.%20Up%20to%20%242%2C500%20in%20interest%20paid%20on%20federal%20and%20many%20private%20student%20loans%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.irs.gov%2Ftaxtopics%2Ftc456%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eis%20deductible%20each%20year%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20individual%20returns%20subject%20to%20income%20limits.%20The%20deduction%20starts%20phasing%20out%20for%20%2475%2C000%20single%20filers%20(%24155%2C000%20for%20joint)%20and%20disappears%20when%20your%20income%20hits%20%2490%2C000%20single%20(%24185%2C000%20joint).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20ballooning%20college%20costs%20and%20record%20educational%20debt%20burdens%2C%20this%20write-off%20softens%20the%20blow%20for%20early-career%20grads%20working%20toward%20financial%20independence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E4.%20Credits%20for%20higher%20education%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.irs.gov%2Fnewsroom%2Ftwo-tax-credits-that-can-help-cover-the-cost-of-higher-education%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520lifetime%2520learning%2520credit%2520is%2Cunlimited%2520number%2520of%2520tax%2520years.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elifetime%20learning%20credit%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20federal%20tax%20credit%20worth%20up%20to%20%242%2C000%20a%20year%20for%20tuition%20and%20educational%20expenses%20paid%20for%20eligible%20college%2C%20university%2C%20or%20vocational%20school%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20the%20more%20commonly%20known%20American%20opportunity%20tax%20credit%2C%20which%20is%20only%20available%20for%20the%20first%20four%20years%20at%20an%20eligible%20school%2C%20the%20lifetime%20learning%20credit%20is%20available%20for%20all%20years%20of%20your%20postsecondary%20education.%20You%20can%20also%20apply%20it%20to%20courses%20to%20acquire%20and%20improve%20job%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20qualify%20for%20the%20lifetime%20learning%20credit%2C%20you%20must%20pursue%20a%20degree%20or%20other%20recognized%20education%20credential.%20The%20credit%20covers%20tuition%2C%20enrollment%20fees%2C%20books%2C%20supplies%2C%20equipment%2C%20and%20other%20education%20expenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20a%20deduction%2C%20which%20just%20reduces%20taxable%20income%2C%20this%20credit%20directly%20reduces%20the%20taxes%20you%20owe.%20But%20it's%20not%20for%20everyone%20%E2%80%94%20this%20credit%20begins%20phasing%20out%20at%20%2480%2C000%20of%20modified%20adjusted%20gross%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E5.%20State%20and%20local%20tax%20deductions%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.irs.gov%2Ftaxtopics%2Ftc503%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etax%20break%3C%2Fa%3E%20allows%20you%20to%20take%20an%20itemized%20deduction%20for%20state%20and%20local%20general%20sales%20taxes%20instead%20of%20deducting%20state%20income%20taxes.%20At%20first%20glance%2C%20this%20might%20seem%20counterintuitive%20%E2%80%94%20why%20wouldn't%20you%20deduct%20state%20income%20tax%2C%20which%20is%20usually%20a%20larger%20sum%3F%20The%20sales%20tax%20deduction%20makes%20sense%20for%20filers%20who%20live%20in%20a%20state%20with%20no%20income%20tax%2C%20such%20as%20Texas%2C%20Florida%2C%20or%20Nevada.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20your%20state%20has%20an%20income%20tax%2C%20you%20may%20still%20come%20ahead%20by%20itemizing%20sales%20tax%20instead%2C%20depending%20on%20your%20tax%20profile.%20The%20IRS%20provides%20tables%20and%20tools%20to%20calculate%20if%20claiming%20sales%20tax%20delivers%20more%20savings%20than%20claiming%20income%20tax.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you've%20recently%20made%20a%20large%20purchase%20subject%20to%20sales%20tax%2C%20like%20a%20boat%2C%20car%2C%20or%20home%20renovation%2C%20this%20could%20help%20lower%20your%20overall%20income%20(and%20tax%20bill).%20Remember%20that%20the%202017%20Tax%20Cuts%20and%20Jobs%20Act%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.irs.gov%2Ftaxtopics%2Ftc503%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecapped%20the%20combined%20total%20deduction%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20%2410%2C000%20per%20taxpayer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E6.%20Child%20and%20dependent%20care%20credit%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20pay%20for%20childcare%20for%20your%20child%20or%20dependent%20%E2%80%94%20like%20day%20camp%2C%20before%20or%20after%20school%20programs%2C%20preschool%2C%20or%20day%20care%20%E2%80%94%20for%20you%20to%20work%2C%20you%20may%20be%20eligible%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.irs.gov%2Fcredits-deductions%2Findividuals%2Fchild-and-dependent-care-credit-information%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChild%20and%20Dependent%20Care%20Credit%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20credit%20covers%20up%20to%2035%25%20of%20%243%2C000%20in%20care%20costs%20for%20one%20qualifying%20dependent%20(%246%2C000%20for%20two%20or%20more%20dependents)%20and%20can%20be%20up%20to%20%241%2C050%20per%20dependent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.irs.gov%2Fcredits-deductions%2Findividuals%2Fchild-tax-credit%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eincome%20restrictions%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20%24200%2C000%20for%20single%20filers%20and%20%24400%2C000%20for%20married%20filing%20jointly.%20But%2C%20this%20tax%20incentive%20can%20help%20offset%20the%20steep%20costs%20working%20parents%20pay%20for%20childcare.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fhow-to-find-financial-advisor%5C%22%3EFinding%20a%20qualified%20financial%20advisor%3C%2Fa%3E%20doesn't%20have%20to%20be%20hard.%20SmartAsset's%20free%20tool%20matches%20you%20with%20up%20to%20three%20fiduciary%20financial%20advisors%20in%20your%20area%20in%20minutes.%20Each%20advisor%20has%20been%20vetted%20by%20SmartAdvisor%20and%20is%20held%20to%20a%20fiduciary%20standard%20to%20act%20in%20your%20best%20interests.%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsmartasset.com%2Fretirement%2Ffind-a-financial-planner%3Futm_source%3Dbusinessinsider%26utm_medium%3Dcpc%26utm_campaign%3Dbus__falc_bicontent%26utm_content%3DBI%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Start%20your%20search%20now.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffinancial-planner-overlooked-tax-credits-deductions-you-should-know-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710415321000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65f20610ce7f1785b2e9600b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffinancial-planner-overlooked-tax-credits-deductions-you-should-know-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22You%20probably%20already%20know%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20tax%20deductions%20you%20can%20take%2C%20but%20you%20might%20be%20missing%20out%20on%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20in%20savings.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Hanna%20Horvath)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffinancial-planner-overlooked-tax-credits-deductions-you-should-know-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Paytm%20Payments%20Bank%20plans%20to%20cut%20about%2020%25%20of%20staff%20as%20business%20halt%20looms%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710415023000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-02%2F18%2Ffull%2F1708278921-4366.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpaytm-pb-may-cut-20-of-staff-co-says-it-s-routine-employee-assessment-124031400674_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Paytm%20Payments%20Bank%20has%20decided%20to%20lay-off%20staff%20in%20certain%20divisions%2C%20including%20operations%2C%20the%20sources%20with%20direct%20knowledge%20of%20the%20matter%20said%22%2C%2