%22%3Cp%3EContinuing%20to%20strengthen%20its%20ranks%20weeks%20before%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20inducted%20Preneet%20Kaur%2C%20suspended%20Congress%20MP%20and%20wife%20of%20former%20Punjab%20chief%20minister%20Amarinder%20Singh%2C%20into%20the%20party.%20Ms%20Kaur%20is%20the%20MP%20from%20Patiala%20and%20is%20likely%20to%20contest%20from%20the%20seat%20on%20a%20BJP%20ticket%20this%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20stepping%20down%20as%20the%20chief%20minister%20in%202021%2C%20Mr%20Singh%20had%20formed%20the%20Punjab%20Lok%20Congress%20and%20then%20merged%20it%20with%20the%20BJP%20the%20following%20year.%20Ms%20Kaur%20was%20suspended%20from%20the%20Congress%20in%20February%20last%20year%20for%20%26quot%3Banti-party%20activities%26quot%3B%20that%20were%20helping%20the%20BJP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJoining%20the%20BJP%20on%20Thursday%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20National%20General%20Secretaries%20Vinod%20Tawde%20and%20Tarun%20Chugh%20and%20the%20party's%20Punjab%20chief%20Sunil%20Jakhar%2C%20who%20was%20also%20in%20the%20Congress%20earlier%2C%20Ms%20Kaur%20praised%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20his%20contribution%20to%20the%20country's%20development.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20happy%20that%20I%20am%20joining%20the%20BJP%20today.%20In%20the%20past%2025%20years%2C%20I%20have%20worked%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20the%20Assembly.%20The%20time%20has%20come%20when%20everyone%20should%20come%20together%20and%20take%20the%20work%20of%20PM%20Modi%20and%20his%20policies%20forward%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Tawde%20said%20the%20inclusion%20of%20leaders%20like%20Preenet%20Kaur%20will%20make%20the%20party%20stronger%20in%20Punjab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPreneet%20Kaur%20ji%20is%20a%20parliamentarian%20who%20has%20proved%20her%20potential%20by%20working%20on%20many%20committees.%20When%20such%20people%20come%20to%20BJP%2C%20especially%20in%20Punjab%20where%20public%20opinion%20is%20being%20formed%20against%20the%20state%20government%2C%20it%20makes%20us%20strong.%20BJP%20is%20emerging%20in%20the%20mind%20of%20the%20common%20Punjabi.%20The%20development%20of%20Punjab%2C%20as%20desired%20by%20PM%20Modi%2C%20will%20become%20stronger%20with%20Preneet%20Kaur%20ji%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20news%20agency%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Ms%20Kaur%20was%20asked%20why%20she%20had%20quit%20the%20Congress%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20want%20to%20go%20into%20the%20past.%20I%20had%20a%20good%20innings%20with%20the%20Congress%20party%20and%20I%20hope%20I%20have%20a%20better%20innings%20with%20the%20BJP.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Patiala%20seat%20has%20been%20won%20by%20Ms%20Kaur%20four%20times%2C%20including%20in%202019%2C%20and%20had%20also%20been%20held%20by%20Amarinder%20Singh%20in%20the%20past.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Kaur's%20exit%20will%20be%20a%20setback%20for%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20had%20won%20eight%20of%20the%2013%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20Punjab%20in%202019%2C%20but%20faces%20a%20challenge%20from%20INDIA%20ally%20AAP%20-%20which%20is%20now%20in%20power%20in%20the%20state%20-%20as%20well%20as%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20agreeing%20on%20seat-sharing%20pacts%20in%20Delhi%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20Goa%20and%20Chandigarh%2C%20the%20AAP%20and%20the%20Congress%20have%20decided%20to%20go%20it%20alone%20in%20Punjab%2C%20where%20they%20are%20currently%20the%20two%20principal%20parties.%20The%20AAP%20also%20released%20a%20list%20of%20eight%20candidates%2C%20including%20five%20state%20ministers%2C%20from%20Punjab%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20is%20trying%20to%20strengthen%20its%20presence%20in%20the%20state%20by%20reviving%20its%20alliance%20with%20the%20Shiromani%20Akali%20Dal%2C%20which%20had%20quit%20the%20NDA%20over%20the%20farmer%20protests%20in%202020.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%2