2F108494832.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fex-pm-nawaz-sharifs-sons-arrest-warrants-in-panama-papers-scandal-linked-cases-cancelled%2Famp_articleshow%2F108494832.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Taken%20India%20For%20A%20Ride'%3A%20Why%20Supreme%20Court's%20Order%20Against%20Patanjali%20Is%20A%20Significant%20Step%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2F09164656%2Framdev.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20February%2027%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Ftaken-for-a-ride-sc-issues-contempt-notice-to-patanjali-ayurved-its-md-over-misleading-ads%5C%22%3E%20issued%20a%20contempt%20notice%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Patanjali%20Ayurved%2C%20the%20company%20founded%20by%20yoga%20guru%20Ramdev%2C%20and%20its%20managing%20director%20Acharya%20Balakrishna.%20This%20notice%20was%20in%20response%20to%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20continued%20dissemination%20of%20misleading%20advertisements%20claiming%20to%20offer%20permanent%20cures%20for%20various%20diseases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20apex%20court%20bench%20consisting%20of%20Justices%20Hima%20Kohli%20and%20Ahsanuddin%20Amanullah%2C%20strongly%20criticised%20Patanjali%20Ayurved%20for%20its%20misleading%20advertising%20practices%20and%20temporarily%20banned%20the%20company%20from%20marketing%20its%20products%20until%20further%20notice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20an%20assurance%20given%20to%20the%20court%20in%20November%202023%2C%20wherein%20the%20company%20promised%20not%20to%20release%20any%20statements%20that%20made%20unsubstantiated%20claims%20about%20medicinal%20efficacy%20or%20criticise%20any%20system%20of%20medicine%2C%20Patanjali%20Ayurved%20persisted%20in%20its%20misleading%20advertisements.%20The%20bench%20remarked%20that%20the%20entire%20nation%20had%20been%20deceived%20by%20these%20actions.%20Furthermore%2C%20the%20apex%20court%20also%20admonished%20the%20Union%20government%20for%20failing%20to%20take%20any%20action%20against%20these%20advertisements%20despite%20being%20aware%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20the%20case%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20goes%20back%20to%20the%20year%202022.%20In%20August%202022%2C%20the%20Indian%20Medical%20Association%20(IMA)%20took%20legal%20action%20in%20response%20to%20a%20Patanjali%20advertisement%20titled%20%E2%80%9CMisconceptions%20spread%20by%20allopathy%3A%20Save%20yourself%20and%20the%20country%20from%20the%20misconceptions%20spread%20by%20pharma%20and%20medical%20industry.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petition%20raised%20two%20main%20concerns%3A%20firstly%2C%20it%20accused%20Patanjali%20of%20consistently%20disseminating%20misinformation%20to%20denigrate%20allopathy%2C%20which%20it%20deemed%20as%20a%20deliberate%20and%20ongoing%20campaign.%20Secondly%2C%20it%20alleged%20that%20Patanjali%20was%20making%20exaggerated%20claims%20about%20the%20efficacy%20of%20its%20drugs%2C%20purportedly%20based%20on%20scientific%20evidence%2C%20which%20contradicted%20regulations%20banning%20such%20advertisements%20in%20the%20country.%20According%20to%20the%20IMA%2C%20these%20statements%20violated%20both%20the%20Drugs%20and%20Other%20Magical%20Remedies%20Act%2C%201954%20(DOMA)%20and%20the%20Consumer%20Protection%20Act%2C%202019%20(CPA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20Patanjali%E2%80%99s%20Divya%20Amla%20Juice%2C%20recommended%20for%20individuals%20with%20diabetes%2C%20and%20Shivlingi%20Beej%20were%20deemed%20of%20%E2%80%98substandard%20quality%E2%80%99%20by%20the%20Ayurveda%20and%20Unani%20Office%20in%20Haridwar%2C%20as%20revealed%20in%20a%20Right%20to%20Information%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20December%202022%2C%20Nepal%E2%80%99s%20drug%20regulator%20blacklisted%20Patanjali%E2%80%99s%20Divya%20Pharmacy%20for%20failing%20to%20adhere%20to%20WHO%E2%80%99s%20drug%20manufacturing%20standards.%20Additional%20reports%20have%20also%20raised%20concerns%20regarding%20Patanjali%E2%80%99s%20questionable%20quality%20control%20measures%20and%20the%20lack%20of%20robust%20clinical%20trial%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20November%2021%2C%202023%2C%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20bench%20comprising%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fsupreme-court-patanjali-baba-ramdev-misleading-advertisements-indian-medical-association-242694%5C%22%3E%20Justices%20Ahsanuddin%20Amanullah%20and%20Prashant%20Kumar%20Mishra%3C%2Fa%3E%20cautioned%20Patanjali%20against%20advertising%20permanent%20cures%20and%20threatened%20to%20levy%20a%20penalty%20of%20Rs%201%20crore%20for%20each%20product%20making%20such%20claims.%20The%20court%20declined%20to%20engage%20in%20the%20%E2%80%9CAllopathy%20v.%20Ayurveda%E2%80%9D%20discourse%20at%20that%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20its%20assurances%20to%20the%20court%2C%20pledging%20no%20violation%20of%20laws%2C%20especially%20regarding%20product%20advertising%2C%20and%20refraining%20from%20making%20disparaging%20remarks%20about%20any%20medical%20system%2C%20Patanjali%20failed%20to%20uphold%20these%20commitments.%20Soon%20after%20the%20hearing%2C%20Baba%20Ramdev%20praised%20Patanjali%20products%20at%20a%20press%20conference%2C%20followed%20by%20advertisements%20appearing%20in%20mainstream%20media%20in%20December%202023%20and%20January%202024.%20These%20actions%20contravened%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20promise%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20strong%20dose%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20recent%20Supreme%20Court%20ruling%20to%20enforce%20a%20ban%20on%20Patanjali%E2%80%99s%20advertisements%20marks%20a%20pivotal%20step%20in%20addressing%20the%20ongoing%20problem%20of%20misleading%20medical%20advertising.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20society%20where%20many%20individuals%20lack%20sufficient%20knowledge%20of%20medical%20science%20and%20tend%20to%20place%20unwarranted%20faith%20in%20unverified%20herbal%20remedies%2C%20such%20advertising%20practices%20present%20a%20considerable%20risk.%20They%20propagate%20misinformation%20and%20may%20endorse%20products%20that%20could%20potentially%20pose%20harm%20to%20consumers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20efforts%20such%20as%20the%20collaboration%20between%20the%20Ministry%20of%20AYUSH%20and%20the%20Advertising%20Standards%20Council%20of%20India%20to%20tackle%20misleading%20advertisements%2C%20Patanjali%20continued%20to%20spread%20misinformation%20unchecked.%20The%20court%E2%80%99s%20intervention%20signifies%20a%20crucial%20move%20towards%20protecting%20public%20health%20and%20ensuring%20accountability%20in%20the%20marketing%20of%20healthcare%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20persisted%20even%20when%20it%20was%20warned%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20as%20early%20as%20November%202023%20to%20cease%20disseminating%20these%20assertions%20or%20risk%20substantial%20fines%20of%20up%20to%20Rs%201%20crore%20for%20each%20product%20featuring%20false%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20court%20reprimanded%20the%20government%20for%20its%20apparent%20negligence%2C%20accusing%20it%20of%20turning%20a%20blind%20eye%20while%20the%20nation%20was%20deceived.%20The%20government%20could%20have%20legally%20compelled%20Patanjali%20to%20retract%20its%20advertisements%2C%20which%20flagrantly%20contravened%20Section%204%20of%20the%20Drugs%20and%20Other%20Magical%20Remedies%20Act%20(DOMA)%2C%201954%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Consumer%20Protection%20Act%2C%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20current%20legal%20framework%2C%20dissemination%20of%20misleading%20advertisements%20carries%20penalties.%20A%20first%20offence%20under%20the%20Drug%20and%20Magic%20Remedies%20(Objectionable%20Advertisements)%20Act%20(DOMA)%20could%20lead%20to%20imprisonment%20for%20six%20months%20and%2For%20a%20fine.%20For%20subsequent%20offences%2C%20the%20punishment%20may%20extend%20to%20one%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConversely%2C%20the%20Consumer%20Protection%20Act%20imposes%20stricter%20consequences%2C%20with%20a%20potential%20imprisonment%20term%20of%20up%20to%20two%20years%20and%20a%20fine%20of%20around%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20for%20violations.%20Repeat%20offences%20escalate%20to%20a%20five-year%20imprisonment%20term%20and%20a%20fine%20of%20approximately%20Rs%2050%20lakh.%20The%20government%20has%20committed%20to%20investigating%20allegations%20and%20proposing%20appropriate%20actions.%20Strengthening%20advertising%20regulations%20for%20both%20Ayurvedic%20and%20over-the-counter%20(OTC)%20allopathic%20drugs%20should%20be%20a%20priority%20in%20this%20regard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20operate%20in%20grey%20areas.%20For%20instance%2C%20DOMA%20does%20not%20recognise%20a%20list%20of%20drugs%20for%20which%20any%20advertisement%20is%20prohibited.%20But%20that%20still%20leaves%20the%20field%20dangerously%20open%20for%20all%20manner%20of%20products%2C%20including%20some%20vaccines.%20As%20for%20advertisements%20for%20ayurvedic%20products%2C%20these%20are%20more%20common%20than%20their%20allopathic%20counterparts%20because%20they%20do%20not%20require%20pre-approval%20or%20any%20stipulation%20of%20minimum%20information%20for%20the%20consumer.%20Indians%20who%20struggle%20with%20medical%20expenses%20are%20particularly%20vulnerable%20to%20the%20growing%20promotion%20of%20an%20%E2%80%9Cindigenous%E2%80%9D%20medical%20system%20supposedly%20offering%20cheaper%20remedies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPatanjali%E2%80%99s%20prosperity%20and%20its%20ability%20to%20evade%20legal%20scrutiny%20highlight%20a%20troubling%20issue%3A%20the%20lack%20of%20accessible%20and%20affordable%20healthcare.%20The%20underprivileged%20find%20themselves%20trapped%2C%20facing%20a%20choice%20between%20enduring%20delayed%20treatment%20from%20conventional%20medicine%20or%20falling%20victim%20to%20misleading%20and%20exploitative%20advertising%2C%20exacerbating%20their%20plight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeceptive%20advertisements%20not%20only%20breach%20legal%20standards%20but%20also%20endanger%20public%20health%20by%20disseminating%20misinformation%20about%20evidence-based%20treatments%20and%20targeting%20vulnerable%20individuals.%20Patanjali%E2%80%99s%20misleading%20advertising%20practices%20are%20acknowledged%20as%20a%20critical%20public%20health%20concern%20demanding%20urgent%20intervention.%20The%20recent%20Supreme%20Court%20ruling%20represents%20a%20positive%20initial%20move%20towards%20overhauling%20the%20regulations%20overseeing%20this%20medical%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EShivanand%20Pandit%20is%20an%20autonomous%20finance%20and%20tax%20adviser.%20He%20has%2028%20years%20of%20experience%20in%20finance%2C%20accounting%2C%20taxation%20laws%2C%20cost%20management%2C%20wealth%20management%2C%20audit%2C%20corporate%20and%20banking%20laws.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710414008000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2F09164656%2Framdev.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fopinion%2Ftaken-india-for-a-ride-why-supreme-courts-order-against-patanjali-is-a-significant-step%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indians%20who%20struggle%20with%20medical%20expenses%20are%20particularly%20vulnerable%20to%20the%20growing%20promotion%20of%20an%20%E2%80%9Cindigenous%E2%80%9D%20medical%20system%20supposedly%20offering%20cheaper%20remedies.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fopinion%2Ftaken-india-for-a-ride-why-supreme-courts-order-against-patanjali-is-a-significant-step%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BRemarkable...%26quot%3B%3A%20UN%20Hails%20India%20Life%20Expectancy%2C%20Per%20Capita%20Income%20Rise%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAverage%20life%20expectancy%20in%20India%20was%2067.7%20years%20in%202022%20-%20up%20from%2062.7%20a%20year%20earlier%20-%20and%20gross%20national%20income%20(GNI%2C%20per%20capita)%20has%20increased%20to%20%246951%2C%20a%20jump%20of%206.3%20per%20cent%20in%2012%20months%2C%20the%20United%20Nation's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fhuman-development-index%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHuman%20Development%20Index%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20HDI%2C%20report%20has%20said.%20The%20HDI%20report%20also%20indicated%20increases%20in%20expected%20years%20of%20schooling%20(to%2012.6%20per%20individual).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20the%20country%20has%20a%20HDI%20score%20of%200.644%20in%202022%2C%20which%20ranks%20it%20134%20of%20193%20in%20the%20UN's%20report%20for%202023%2F24%20-%20'Breaking%20the%20Gridlock%3A%20Reimagining%20Cooperation%20in%20a%20Polarised%20World'.%20This%20places%20it%20in%20the%20'medium%20human%20development'%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESignificantly%2C%20India's%20HDI%20score%20for%202022%20saw%20an%20increase%20after%20a%20drop%20the%20year%20before%20and%20a%20flat%20trend%20in%20the%20years%20prior.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHDI%20refers%20to%20assessment%20of%20average%20achievements%20in%20three%20basic%20dimensions%20of%20human%20development%20-%20long%20and%20healthy%20life%2C%20access%20to%20education%2C%20and%20decent%20standard%20of%20living.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%201990%20HDI%20was%200.434%2C%20making%20the%202022%20score%20a%20positive%20change%20of%20nearly%2049%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-drops-one-more-rank-in-development-index-now-at-132-3327232%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIn%202021%20Report%2C%C2%A0India%20Drops%20Another%20Rank%20In%20Development%20Index%2C%20Now%20132%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20has%20shown%20remarkable%20progress%20in%20human%20development%20over%20the%20years.%20Since%201990%2C%20life%20expectancy%20at%20birth%20has%20risen%20by%209.1%20years%3B%20expected%20years%20of%20schooling%20have%20increased%20by%204.6%20years%3B%20and%20mean%20years%20of%20schooling%20have%20grown%20by%203.8%20years.%20India's%20GNI%20per%20capita%20has%20grown%20by%20approximately%20287%20per%20cent%2C%26quot%3B%20Caitlin%20Wiesen%2C%20the%20United%20Nations%20Development%20Programme's%20country%20representative%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EGender%20Inequality%20Report%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20also%20said%20India%20had%20demonstrated%20%26quot%3Bprogress%20in%20reducing%20gender%20inequality%26quot%3B%2C%20flagging%20a%20Gender%20Inequality%20Index%2C%20or%20GII%2C%20of%200.437%2C%20which%20is%20better%20than%20the%20global%20average.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20GII%20list%2C%20which%20ranks%20countries%20on%20three%20key%20dimensions%20-%20reproductive%20health%2C%20empowerment%2C%20and%20labour%20market%20participation%20-%20India%20places%20108%20of%20166%20nations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReproductive%20healthcare%20is%20better%20than%20other%20countries%20in%20the%20'medium%20HDI'%20category%2C%20and%20the%202022%20adolescent%20birth%20rate%20was%2016.3%20(births%20per%201%2C000%20women%20aged%2015-19)%20-%20an%20improvement%20from%2017.1%20from%202021.%20There%20is%2C%20however%2C%20a%20gap%20of%2047.8%20per%20cent%20in%20labour%20force%20participation%20rates%20of%20men%20and%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-ranks-131-in-uns-human-development-index-2339643%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndia%20Drops%20One%20Spot%20To%20131%20In%20UN's%20Human%20Development%20Index%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20highlights%20the%20country's%20commitment%20over%20time%20to%20mprove%20the%20quality%20of%20life%20for%20its%20citizens.%20But%20there%20is%20room%20for%20improvement.%20With%20a%20renewed%20focus%20on%20women-led%20development%2C%20India%20can%20further%20unlock%20socio-economic%20progress%2C%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20a%20more%20equitable%20future%20for%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Wiesen%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20attributed%20the%20improvements%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bdecisive%20agenda...%20to%20ensure%20women's%20empowerment%20through%20policy%20initiatives%20aimed%20at%20long-term%20socio-economic%20and%20political%20development%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGovernment%20initiatives%20have%20spanned%20across%20women's%20lifecycles%20including%20large%20scale%20initiatives%20for%20girls'%20education%2C%20skill%20development%2C%20entrepreneurship%20facilitation%20and%20safety%20in%20the%20workplace%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Women%20and%20Child%20Development%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EGlobal%20HDI%20Values%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20global%20HDI%20values%20have%20fallen%20for%20the%20second%20consecutive%20year%3B%20this%20is%20the%20first%20time%20that%20has%20happened.%20The%20UN%20has%20red-flagged%20growing%20inequality%20between%20rich%20and%20poor%20countries%20in%20this%20regard%2C%20a%20crisis%20driven%20by%20the%20continuing%20impact%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBefore%20the%20crisis%2C%20the%20world%20was%20on%20track%20to%20reach%20an%20average%20'very%20high'%20HDI%20by%202030%2C%20coinciding%20with%20the%20deadline%20for%20the%20Sustainable%20Development%20Goals%20(SDGs).%20Now%20we%20are%20off%20track%2C%20with%20every%20region%20running%20below%20its%20pre-2019%20projections%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpandemic-set-human-development-back-by-5-years-globally-un-report-3325899%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPandemic%20Set%20Human%20Development%20Back%20By%205%20Years%20Globally%3A%20UN%20Report%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEssentially%2C%20the%20world%20has%20not%20reached%20human%20development%20levels%20expected%20by%20this%20time%20because%20of%20Covid%2C%20and