ENow%2C%20under%20fire%20for%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20rules%20for%20the%20CAA%20being%20announced%20by%20the%20Home%20Ministry%2C%20at%20the%20eve%20of%20the%20general%20elections%20and%20four%20years%20and%20three%20months%20after%20the%20Act%20was%20passed%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_fr5vWV3K04%26ab_channel%3DBharatiyaJanataParty%5C%22%3EShah%20shied%20away%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20speaking%20about%20the%20sequence%20of%20CAA%20leading%20to%20the%20NRC.%20Dodging%20the%20question%20on%20chronology%2C%20that%20his%20forceful%20mentions%20had%20pushed%20into%20political%20folklore%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20NRC%20now%2C%20talk%20only%20about%20the%20CAA.%E2%80%9D%20He%20asked%20ANI%20to%20not%20%E2%80%9Cmix%E2%80%9D%20the%20two%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CAkhand%20Bharat%E2%80%9D%20logic%20for%20CAA%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20podcast%20out%20earlier%20today%2C%20Shah%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20Akhand%20Bharat%2C%20all%20the%20religious%20minorities%20who%20had%20been%20persecuted%2C%20we%20have%20a%20duty%20to%20protect%20and%20offer%20refuge%20to.%E2%80%9D%20On%20Muslim%20groups%20like%20Hazaras%2C%20Shias%20or%20Ahmadiyas%20being%20possibly%20persecuted%20in%20those%20countries%2C%20Shah%20refused%20to%20accept%20that%20they%20were%20persecuted%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CAfghanistan%2C%20Pakistan%20and%20Bangladesh%20are%20Islamic%20countries.%20We%20have%20no%20data%20on%20the%20persecution.%20How%20can%20Muslims%20be%20persecuted%20there%3F%E2%80%9D%20Calling%20the%20law%20as%20one%20tied%20with%20India%E2%80%99s%20past%2C%20Shah%20said%20Muslims%20were%20allowed%20to%20seek%20citizenship%20under%20other%20laws%2C%20but%20the%20CAA%20fast-tracked%20citizenship%20for%20non-Muslim%20minorities%20from%20three%20countries%20in%20South%20Asia%20who%20had%20come%20into%20the%20country%20before%20December%202019%20and%20had%20been%20residing%20in%20India%20for%20five%20ye