3E%3Cp%3EMortgage%20rates%20aren't%20directly%20impacted%20by%20changes%20to%20the%20federal%20funds%20rate%2C%20but%20they%20often%20trend%20up%20or%20down%20ahead%20of%20Fed%20policy%20moves.%20This%20is%20because%20mortgage%20rates%20change%20based%20on%20investor%20demand%20for%20mortgage-backed%20securities%2C%20and%20this%20demand%20is%20often%20impacted%20by%20how%20investors%20expect%20Fed%20hikes%20to%20affect%20the%20broader%20economy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20that%20the%20Fed%20has%20paused%20hiking%20rates%2C%20mortgage%20rates%20have%20come%20down%20a%20bit.%20Once%20the%20Fed%20starts%20cutting%20rates%2C%20which%20is%20likely%20to%20happen%20this%20year%2C%20mortgage%20rates%20should%20fall%20even%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-mortgage-refinance-rates-today-thursday-14-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710410401000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F628512b5e19cda0018866eee%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-mortgage-refinance-rates-today-thursday-14-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22These%20are%20today's%20mortgage%20and%20refinance%20rates.%20Mortgage%20rates%20are%20down%20a%20little%20bit%20from%20last%20month%2C%20and%20they%20should%20fall%20further%20throughout%202024%20and%202025.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Molly%20Grace)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-mortgage-refinance-rates-today-thursday-14-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Curtis%20Brown%20Group%20Taps%20Martha%20Atack%20to%20Lead%20New%20Unscripted%20and%20Entertainment%20Division%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710410400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FMartha-Atack-Curt