he%20report%20states%20that%20franchise%20feel%20that%20such%20sudden%20decisions%20taken%20by%20cricketers%20can%20upset%20the%20auction%20strategies%20in%20place%20for%20the%20different%20teams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrook%20on%20Wednesday%20said%20he%20has%20pulled%20out%20of%20the%20upcoming%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20because%20he%20wants%20to%20be%20around%20his%20grieving%20family%20after%20the%20death%20of%20his%20grandmother.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrook's%20grandmother%20died%20in%20February.%20%26quot%3BI%20can%20confirm%20that%20I%20have%20made%20the%20very%20difficult%20decision%20not%20to%20play%20in%20the%20upcoming%20IPL%2C%26quot%3B%20Brook%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20so%20excited%20to%20be%20picked%20by%20Delhi%20Capitals%20and%20was%20so%20looking%20forward%20to%20joining%20up%20with%20everyone.%20Whilst%20I%20don't%20think%20I%20should%20need%20to%20share%20my%20personal%20reasons%20behind%20this%20decision%2C%20I%20know%20there%20will%20be%20many%20asking%20why.%20So%20I%20do%20want%20to%20share%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20lost%20my%20grandmother%20last%20month%20-%20she%20was%20a%20rock%20to%20me%20and%20I%20spent%20a%20huge%20amount%20of%20my%20childhood%20in%20her%20home%3B%20my%20attitude%20to%20life%20and%20love%20for%20cricket%20was%20shaped%20by%20her%20and%20my%20late%20grandfather%2C%26quot%3B%20the%2025-year-old%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20inaugural%20IPL%20season%20last%20year%2C%20Brook%20set%20the%20stage%20on%20fire%20with%20a%2055-ball%20hundred%20against%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20only%20to%20end%20on%20an%20underwhelming%20note.%20In%20all%2C%20he%20managed%20only%20190%20runs%20for%20the%20Sunrisers%20Hyderabad%20in%2011%20matches%20after%20the%20franchise%20paid%20Rs%2013.25%20crore%20to%20acquire%20his%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(With%20PTI%20inputs)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710405240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-04%2