ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20three-member%20selection%20panel%20headed%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20Thursday%20(March%2014)%20appointed%20two%20former%20Indian%20Administrative%20Service%20officers%20%E2%80%93%20Gyanesh%20Kumar%20and%20Sukhbir%20Singh%20Sandhu%20%E2%80%93%20as%20election%20commissioners.%20Before%20their%20appointment%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20had%20been%20down%20to%20just%20one%20member%2C%20chief%20election%20commissioner%20Rajiv%20Kumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKumar%20retired%20as%20Union%20secretary%20for%20cooperation%2C%20a%20ministry%20headed%20by%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fgovt-sets-up-dedicated-desk-to-look-after-ayodhya-issue-790751.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEarlier%2C%20he%20was%20in%20the%20Union%20home%20ministry%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20he%20handled%20the%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20as%20well%20as%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20Ayodhya%20verdict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESandhu%20was%20chief%20secretary%20of%20Uttarakhand%20till%20the%20end%20of%20January%202024.%20As%20the%20top%20bureaucrat%20in%20the%20state%2C%20he%20would%20have%20overseen%20the%20drafting%20of%20its%20controversial%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%2C%20which%20was%20passed%20by%20the%20legislature%20a%20week%20after%20he%20retired.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElection%20commissioner%20Arun%20Goel%20had%20abruptly%20resigned%20from%20his%20position%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20and%20the%20reasons%20for%20his%20resignation%20remain%20unknown.%20Another%20election%20commissioners%2C%20Anup%20Pandey%2C%20retired%20on%20February%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20opposition%20member%20in%20the%20selection%20panel%20%E2%80%93%20Congress%20leader%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%20%E2%80%93%20said%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fformer-ias-officers-gyanesh-kumar-sukhbir-singh-sandhu-picked-election-commissioners-by-pm-led-panel-9213830%2F%5C%22%3Eexpressed%20his%20dissent%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Thursday%E2%80%99s%20appointments%2C%20questioning%20the%20process%20followed.%20He%20told%20reporters%20that%20the%20shortlist%20of%20candidates%20was%20not%20made%20available%20to%20him%20in%20advance%2C%20and%20that%20he%20was%20only%20given%20a%20list%20of%20212%20officers%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20terms%20of%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprsindia.org%2Fbilltrack%2Fthe-chief-election-commissioner-and-other-election-commissioners-appointment-conditions-of-service-and-term-of-office-bill-2023%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChief%20Election%20Commissioner%20and%20Other%20Election%20Commissioners%20(Appointment%2C%20Conditions%20of%20Service%20and%20Term%20of%20Office)%20Act%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20government-dominated%20selection%20committee%20is%20empowered%20to%20fill%20vacant%20slots%20on%20the%20ECI%20from%20candidates%20short-listed%20by%20a%20search%20committee%20headed%20by%20the%20Union%20cabinet%20secretary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Act%20is%20under%20challenge%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20for%20violating%20the%20apex%20court%E2%80%99s%20ruling%20last%20year%20that%20ECI%20members%20be%20selected%20by%20a%20panel%20that%20is%20not%20dominated%20by%20the%20government%20%E2%80%93%20so%20as%20to%20ensure%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20independence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20new%20appointments%20come%20at%20a%20time%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ffive-reasons-theres-a-dark-cloud-over-election-commissions-transparency-and-functioning%5C%22%3Equestions%20have%20been%20raised%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20the%20independent%20functioning%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission%2C%20ahead%20of%20the%20crucial%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20overseeing%20and%20ensuring%20free%20and%20fair%20voting%20in%20all%20543%20parliamentary%20constituencies%2C%20the%20three%20election%20commissioners%20are%20tasked%20with%20making%20sure%20all%20political%20parties%20and%20leaders%20stick%20to%20the%20letter%20and%20spirit%20of%20the%20election%20law%2C%20especially%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%2C%20which%20prohibits%20the%20misuse%20of%20government%20machinery%20by%20ruling%20parties%20as%20well%20as%20the%20use%20of%20appeals%20to%20religion%20and%20hate%20speech%20as%20a%20means%20of%20gathering%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20announcement%20also%20came%20on%20the%20same%20day%20when%20a%20high-level%20panel%20headed%20by%20former%20President%20Ram%20Nath%20Kovind%20submitted%20its%20report%20on%20simultaneous%20elections%20to%20the%20current%20president.%20The%20committee%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fonoe.gov.in%2FHLC-Report-hi%23flipbook-df_manual_book%2F1%2F%5C%22%3Ehas%20recommended%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20elections%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20state%20legislative%20assemblies%20should%20take%20place%20simultaneously.%20Following%20this%2C%20elections%20to%20municipalities%20and%20panchayats%20should%20be%20held%20within%20100%20days%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710404994000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F06152712%2FElection-Commission-of-India-Photo-PTI1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmodi-led-panel-appoints-ex-ias-officers-gyanesh-kumar-sukhbir-singh-sandhu-as-election-commissioners%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20only%20opposition%20member%20in%20the%20selection%20panel%20%E2%80%93%20Congress%20leader%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%20%E2%80%93%20has%20expressed%20his%20dissent%20on%20Thursday's%20appointments%2C%20questioning%20the%20process%20followed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%