eople%20of%20Ladakh%20should%20have%20the%20right%20to%20run%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20with%20bureaucratic%20rule%20in%20the%20newly%20established%20Union%20territory%2C%20leaders%20in%20Leh%20also%20realised%20that%20in%20the%20process%20of%20reorganisation%2C%20the%20people%20of%20Ladakh%20had%20lost%20a%20say%20in%20the%20decision-making%20process.%20While%20day-to-day%20decisions%20are%20being%20made%20by%20the%20bureaucracy%20led%20by%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%2C%20larger%20policy%20decisions%20are%20being%20made%20by%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs.%20There%20are%20many%20instances%20where%20the%20decisions%20were%20taken%20by%20the%20UT%20administration%20without%20even%20consulting%20the%20Ladakh%20Autonomous%20Hill%20Development%20Council.%20Now%20both%20councils%20are%20almost%20disempowered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20the%20fund%20flow%20was%20not%20adequate%2C%20given%20that%20J%26amp%3BK%20itself%20was%20dependent%20on%20central%20grants.%20However%2C%20Ladakh%20had%20fair%20representation%20in%20the%20Government%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20with%20four%20Members%20of%20Legislative%20Assemblies%20and%20two%20members%20of%20Legislative%20Councils.%20At%20times%2C%20there%20were%20two%20Ministers%20in%20the%20Cabinet%20and%20one%20Minister%20of%20State%20from%20Ladakh%20in%20the%20Government%20of%20J%26amp%3BK.%20Given%20that%20the%20population%20was%20two%20lakh%20seventy-four%20thousand%2C%20the%20representation%20was%20adequate%20to%20translate%20the%20aspirations%20of%20people%20into%20policy%20decisions%20and%20enough%20to%20influence%20the%20business%20transacted%20by%20bureaucracy%20to%20address%20day-to-day%20grievances%20of%20the%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPublic%20employment%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegarding%20the%20share%20of%20Ladakhi%20people%20in%20public%20employment%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20note%20that%20young%20people%20from%20Leh%20and%20Kargil%20usually%20obtained%20a%20fair%20share%20in%20the%20gazetted%20posts%20advertised%20by%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Public%20Service%20Commission.%20The%20erstwhile%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20being%20a%20state%20with%20robust%20government%20machinery%2C%20had%20a%20large%20number%20of%20posts%2C%20and%20vacancies%20were%20advertised%20every%20year.%20The%20young%20educated%20youth%20from%20Leh%20and%20Kargil%20participated%20in%20these%20recruitments%20with%20great%20enthusiasm.%20After%202010%2C%20the%20selection%20percentage%20of%20these%20educated%20youth%20was%20higher%2C%20given%20the%20greater%20investment%20of%20Ladakhi%20parents%20in%20their%20children%20sending%20them%20to%20good%20schools%20and%20colleges%20across%20India%20despite%20domestic%20hardships.%20Many%20candidates%20were%20selected%20as%20assistant%20professors%20and%20lecturers%2C%20and%20some%20even%20served%20in%20the%20colleges%20of%20Srinagar%20and%20Jammu.%20The%20selections%20in%20the%20prestigious%20Kashmir%20Administrative%20Service%20also%20witnessed%20a%20spike%20from%202008%20to%202019%2C%20and%20selections%20were%20witnessed%20in%20each%20batch.%20Ladakhi%20people%20began%20celebrating%20that%20their%20own%20educated%20youth%20were%20teaching%20in%20their%20colleges%20and%20taking%20the%20reins%20of%20bureaucracy.%20However%2C%20on%20August%205%2C%202019%2C%20public%20employment%20came%20to%20a%20standstill%2C%20leaving%20the%20uneducated%20youth%20and%20their%20ageing%20parents%20high%20and%20dry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20separation%20of%20Ladakh%20from%20J%26amp%3BK%20and%20the%20introduction%20of%20Domicile%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20cut%20this%20umbilical%20cord%20of%20public%20employment%20opportunities%20to%20the%20youth%20of%20Ladakh.%20Added%20to%20this%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20has%20failed%20miserably%20to%20put%20in%20place%20corresponding%20systems%20of%20gazetted%20recruitment%20in%20Ladakh.%20If%20one%20more%20year%20passes%20without%20recruitment%2C%20this%20will%20be%20a%20criminal%20act%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20to%20deprive%20the%20already%20disadvantaged%20youth%20of%20Ladakh%20of%20public%20employment%20opportunities%20in%20their%20own%20Union%20territory%20for%20five%20years%20since%20the%20establishment%20of%20the%20UT.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%20on%20March%204%2C%20before%20meeting%20with%20the%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20when%20both%20Leh%20Apex%20Body%20and%20Kargil%20Democratic%20Alliance%20were%20met%20with%20the%20MHA%20officials%20they%20were%20principally%20agreed%20to%20give%2080%25%20reservations%20in%20Gazetted%20jobs%20to%20the%20ST%20holders%20of%20Ladakh%20while%20they%20have%20also%20agreed%20to%20extend%20the%20JKPSC%20to%20Ladakh%20also.%20However%2C%20both%20of%20these%20issues%20have%20not%20been%20notified%20yet%2C%20which%20is%20again%20giving%20a%20sense%20of%20deprivation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20also%20a%20fact%20that%20the%20leaders%20in%20Leh%20district%20of%20Ladakh%20who%20have%20struggled%20for%20the%20UT%20status%20for%20Ladakh%20are%20now%20feeling%20that%20Ladakh%20was%20better%20off%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20than%20in%20the%20current%20UT%20while%20as%20in%20Kargil%20people%20were%20expecting%20the%20same%20situation%20even%20before%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20UT%20of%20Ladakh.%C2%A0%20People%20think%20that%20their%20identity%2C%20culture%20and%20land%20are%20in%20danger%20and%20for%20that%20they%20are%20demanding%20safeguards%20under%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20environmental%20activist%20Sonam%20Wangchuk%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20have%20no%20democracy%2C%20no%20voting%20rights%20to%20elect%20their%20representatives%20to%20an%20Assembly.%20It%20is%20like%20a%20colony%20in%20the%20olden%20times%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UT%20without%20legislature%20and%20safeguards%20and%20the%20youths%20without%20having%20adequate%20jobs%20is%20giving%20a%20sense%20of%20insecurity%20among%20the%20people%20in%20Ladakh.%20Ladakhis%20in%20general%20are%20now%20feeling%20betrayed%20by%20the%20government.%20This%20growing%20sense%20of%20betrayal%20is%20indicating%20that%20Ladakh%20is%20a%20new%20headache%20therefore%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20must%20take%20the%20Ladakh%20issue%20seriously%20and%20fulfill%20the%20aspirations%20of%20the%20people%20positively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESajjad%20Kargili%20is%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Kargil%20Democratic%20Alliance%20and%20the%20High-Powered%20Committee.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710404645000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F14134644%2F14-Feb-2023-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwith-ladakh-as-ut-local-youth-lost-all-access-to-public-employment%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20separation%20of%20Ladakh%20from%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%20the%20introduction%20of%20domicile%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20cut%20off%20an%20umbilical%20cord%20of%20public%20employment%20opportunities%20to%20the%20youth%20of%20Ladakh.%20Added%20to%20this%2C%20Union%20home%20ministry%20has%20failed%20miserably%20to%20put%20in%20place%20corresponding%20systems%20of%20recruitment%20for%20gazetted%20posts%20in%20Ladakh.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwith-ladakh-as-ut-local-youth-lost-all-access-to-public-employment%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Timoth%C3%A9e%20Chalamet%20to%20raise%20his%20fee%20after%20Dune%202%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710404353000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108488806%2Cimgsize-17008.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fhollywood%2Fnews%2Ffollowing-the-success-of-dune-part-2-timothe-chalamet-to-raise-his-fee%2Farticleshow%2F108488650.cms%22%2C%22s