e%20has%20been%20staging%20one-off%20shows%20across%20the%20United%20States%20in%20anticipation%20of%20his%20new%20album%20%E2%80%9CEverything%20I%20Thought%20It%20Was%2C%E2%80%9D%20out%20this%20Friday%2C%20bringing%20lively%20performances%20to%20his%20native%20Memphis%20and%20New%20York%20City.%20But%20those%20who%20were%20lucky%20enough%20to%20snag%20a%20free%20ticket%20to%20attend%20his%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Steven%20J.%20Horowitz%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Fmusic%2Fnews%2Fjustin-timberlake-nsync-reunion-los-angeles-performance-1235941618%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Fmusic%2Fnews%2Fjustin-timberlake-nsync-reunion-los-angeles-performance-1235941618%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Fmusic%2Fnews%2Fjustin-timberlake-nsync-reunion-los-angeles-performance-1235941618%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Government%20Blocks%2018%20Streaming%20Platforms%20In%20India%20Over%20'Obscene'%20Content%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20Information%20%26amp%3B%20Broadcasting%20(I%26amp%3BB)%20has%20taken%20action%2C%20in%20coordination%20with%20various%20intermediaries%2C%20to%20block%2018%20OTT%20platforms%20publishing%20%26quot%3Bobscene%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3Bvulgar%2C%26quot%3B%20and%2C%20in%20some%20instances%2C%20%26quot%3Bpornographic%20content%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E19%20websites%2C%2010%20apps%20(7%20on%20the%20Google%20Play%20Store%20and%203%20on%20the%20Apple%20App%20Store)%2C%20and%2057%20social%20media%20accounts%20associated%20with%20these%20platforms%20have%20been%20disabled%20for%20public%20access%20in%20India%2C%20an%20official%20statement%20from%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Information%20and%20Broadcasting%20said%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20Minister%20for%20Information%20%26amp%3B%20Broadcasting%20Anurag%20Singh%20Thakur%20has%20repeatedly%20emphasized%20the%20responsibility%20of%20the%20platforms%20to%20not%20propagate%20obscenity%2C%20vulgarity%20and%20abuse%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20'creative%20expression'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%2012%2C%20Mr%20Thakur%20announced%20that%2018%20OTT%20platforms%20publishing%20obscene%20and%20vulgar%20content%20had%20been%20taken%20down%2C%20the%20release%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20further%20added%20that%20the%20recent%20decision%20was%20taken%20under%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20Information%20Technology%20Act%2C%202000%2C%20in%20consultation%20with%20other%20ministries%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20India%2C%20and%20domain%20experts%20specializing%20in%20media%20and%20entertainment%2C%20women's%20rights%2C%20and%20child%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20significant%20portion%20of%20the%20content%20hosted%20on%20these%20platforms%20was%20found%20to%20be%20obscene%2C%20vulgar%2C%20and%20portrayed%20women%20in%20a%20demeaning%20manner.%20It%20depicted%20nudity%20and%20sexual%20acts%20in%20various%20inappropriate%20contexts%2C%20such%20as%20relationships%20between%20teachers%20and%20students%2C%20incestuous%20family%20relationships%2C%20etc.%20The%20content%20included%20sexual%20innuendos%20and%2C%20in%20some%20instances%2C%20prolonged%20segments%20of%20pornographic%20and%20sexually%20explicit%20scenes%20devoid%20of%20any%20thematic%20or%20societal%20relevance%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20content%20was%20determined%20to%20be%20prima%20facie%20in%20violation%20of%20Sections%2067%20and%2067A%20of%20the%20IT%20Act%2C%20Section%20292%20of%20the%20IPC%2C%20and%20Section%204%20of%20the%20Indecent%20Representation%20of%20Women%20(Prohibition)%20Act%2C%201986%2C%20the%20release%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20OTT%20apps%20amassed%20more%20than%201%20crore%20downloads%2C%20while%20two%20others%20had%20over%2050%20lakh%20downloads%20on%20the%20Google%20Play%20Store.%20Additionally%2C%20these%20OTT%20platforms%20extensively%20utilize%20social%20media%20to%20disseminate%20trailers%2C%20specific%20scenes%2C%20and%20external%20links%20aimed%20at%20attracting%20audiences%20to%20their%20websites%20and%20apps.%20The%20social%20media%20accounts%20of%20the%20concerned%20OTT%20platforms%20had%20a%20cumulative%20followership%20of%20over%2032%20lakh%20users%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20I%26amp%3BB%20consistently%20conducts%20sensitization%20efforts%20with%20OTT%20platforms%20and%20their%20self-regulatory%20bodies%20established%20under%20the%20IT%20Rules%2C%202021%20through%20meetings%2C%20webinars%2C%20workshops%2C%20etc%2C%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Government%20of%20India%20remains%20committed%20to%20fostering%20the%20growth%20and%20development%20of%20the%20OTT%20industry.%20Several%20measures%20have%20been%20undertaken%20in%20this%20regard%2C%20including%20the%20introduction%20of%20the%20Inaugural%20OTT%20Award%20for%20Web%20Series%20at%20the%2054th%20International%20Film%20Festival%20of%20India%2C%20collaboration%20with%20OTT%20platforms%20in%20the%20media%20and%20entertainment%20sector%2C%20and%20the%20establishment%20of%20a%20light%20touch%20regulatory%20framework%20with%20an%20emphasis%20on%20self-regulation%20under%20the%20IT%20Rules%2C%202021%2C%20the%20release%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710400920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-05%2Ftmcj0cnk_pornography-generic_625x300_29_May_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgovernment-blocks-18-streaming-platforms-in-india-over-obscene-content-5236230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Ministry%20of%20Information%20%26amp%3B%20Broadcasting%20(I%26amp%3BB)%20has%20taken%20action%2C%20in%2