le%22%3A%22LIVE%20news%3A%20Wholesale%20inflation%20eases%20to%200.2%25%20in%20Feb%20from%200.27%25%20in%20Jan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710399874000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2022-06%2F10%2Ffull%2F1654843180-8238.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Flatest-news-live-on-march-14-todays-breaking-news-updates-droupadi-murmu-farmers-protest-124031400076_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Latest%20news%20updates%3A%20Catch%20all%20the%20news%20updates%20from%20around%20the%20world%20here%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Flatest-news-live-on-march-14-todays-breaking-news-updates-droupadi-murmu-farmers-protest-124031400076_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Flatest-news-live-on-march-14-todays-breaking-news-updates-droupadi-murmu-farmers-protest-124031400076_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Flatest-news-live-on-march-14-todays-breaking-news-updates-droupadi-murmu-farmers-protest-124031400076_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Australian%20Billionaire%20Unveils%20New%20Plans%20For%20'Titanic%20II'%20To%20Sail%20In%202027%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EClive%20Palmer%2C%20an%20Australian%20mining%20billionaire%2C%20has%20announced%20his%20plans%20to%20build%20a%20replica%20of%20the%20most%20famous%20cruise%20ship%20in%20history%2C%20the%20Titanic.%20According%20to%20a%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2024%2F03%2F13%2Ftravel%2Faustralia-clive-palmer-relaunches-titanic-two-intl-hnk%2Findex.html%5C%22%3ECNN%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%2C%C2%A0Mr%20Palmer%20who%20first%20announced%20his%20plans%20in%202012%20and%20again%20in%202018%2C%20resurrected%20his%20passion%20project%20to%20build%20a%20replica%20of%20the%20ship%20during%20an%20event%20at%20the%20Sydney%20Opera%20House%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Palmer%20said%20his%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bluestarline.com.au%2F%5C%22%3EBlue%20Star%20Line%20%3C%2Fa%3Enow%20intends%20to%20build%20the%20replica%20ship%20and%20set%20sail%20in%20June%202027.%C2%A0''We%20are%20very%20pleased%20to%20announce%20that%20after%20unforeseen%20global%20delays%2C%20we%20have%20re-engaged%20with%20partners%20to%20bring%20the%20dream%20of%20Titanic%20ll%20to%20life.%20Let%20the%20journey%20begin%2C''%20Mr%20Palmer%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''The%20government%20lockdowns%20sent%20the%20cruise%20industry%20into%20a%20long-term%20shutdown%2C%20We%20are%20getting%20the%20best%20ship-builders%2C%20designers%20and%20engineers%20in%20the%20world%20back%20on%20deck%20to%20build%20Titanic%20II%2C''%20he%20further%20said.%C2%A0The%20billionaire%20claimed%C2%A0that%20this%20ship%20would%20be%20''far%2C%20far%20superior%20to%20the%20original''.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''It's%20a%20lot%20more%20fun%20to%20do%20the%20Titanic%20than%20it%20is%20to%20sit%20at%20home%20and%20count%20my%20money%2C''%20Mr%20Palmer%20told%20local%20media.%20The%20mining%20mogul%C2%A0has%20a%20net%20worth%20of%20%244.2%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETenders%20are%20now%20being%20sought%20to%20build%20the%20ship%2C%20and%20Mr%20Palmer%20hopes%20to%20find%20a%20shipbuilder%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year%20to%20enable%20work%20to%20begin%20in%202025.%C2%A0There%20will%20be%20room%20for%202%2C345%20passengers%20on%20board%20with%20835%20cabins%20across%20nine%20decks.%20Almost%20half%20of%20the%20rooms%20will%20be%20reserved%20for%20first-class%20passengers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ship%20would%20have%20the%20same%20interiors%20and%20cabin%20layout%20as%20the%20original%20vessel%2C%20complete%20with%20a%20ballroom%2C%20swimming%20pool%20and%20Turkish%20baths.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''In%201912%20the%20Titanic%20was%20the%20ship%20of%20dreams.%20For%20over%20a%20century%20Titanic's%20legend%20has%20been%20powered%20by%20mystery%2C%20intrigue%20and%20respect%20for%20all%20she%20stood%20for%2C''%20Mr%20Palmer%20said.%C2%A0He%20estimated%20the%2056%2C000-tonne%20ship%20would%20cost%20between%20%24500m%20and%20%241%20billion%2C%20as%20per%20a%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Faustralia-news%2F2024%2Fmar%2F13%2Fclive-palmer-titanic-ii-relaunch-plans-sydney-opera-house%5C%22%3EGuardian%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20report.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''Titanic%20II%20is%20something%20that%20needed%20to%20be%20built.%20We%20all%20know%20how%20to%20make%20war.%20We%20get%20armies%20and%20we%20fund%20wars.%20People%20know%20about%20that.%20But%20it%20is%20a%20lot%20harder%20to%20make%20peace.%20To%20make%20peace%20you%20have%20got%20to%20stick%20with%20it%20every%20day.%20You%20progress%20inch%20by%20inch%2C''%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ship's%20maiden%20voyage%20is%20intended%20to%20trace%20the%20original%20route%20of%20the%20infamous%201912%20voyage%20from%20Southampton%20to%20New%20York.%20It%20is%20scheduled%20for%202027.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%C2%A0The%20RMS%20Titanic%2C%C2%A0a%20British%20passenger%20liner%2C%20was%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20and%20most%20luxurious%20ocean%20liners%20ever%20built.%C2%A0The%20ship%20was%20on%20its%20maiden%20voyage%20from%20Southampton%20to%20New%20York%20City%20and%20had%C2%A02%2C240%20passengers%20and%20crew%20on%20board.%20On%C2%A0April%2015%2C%201912%2C%20the%20ship%20collided%20with%20a%20massive%20iceberg%20and%20sank%20in%20less%20than%20three%20hours.%20Over%201%2C500%20people%20died%20in%20the%20maritime%20disaster%2C%20while%20only%20705%20individuals%20survived.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tragedy%20inspired%20James%20Cameron's%20Oscar-winning%201997%20blockbuster%3Cem%3E%20'Titanic'%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20starring%20Leonardo%20DiCaprio%20and%20Kate%20Winslet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710399420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fke693i48_titanic-ii_625x300_14_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwill-be-far-superior-australian-billionaire-unveils-new-plans-for-titanic-ii-to-sail-in-2027-5235925%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20RMS%20Titanic%2C%20a%20British%20passenger%20liner%2C%20collided%20with%20a%20massive%20iceberg%20and%20sank%20in%20less%20than%20three%20hours%20on%20April%2015%2C%201912.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwill-be-far-superior-australian-billionaire-unveils-new-plans-for-titanic-ii-to-sail-in-2027-5235925%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwill-be-far-superior-australian-billionaire-unveils-new-plans-for-titanic-ii-to-sail-in-2027-5235925%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwill-be-far-superior-australian-billionaire-unveils-new-plans-for-titanic-ii-to-sail-in-2027-5235925%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20BJP%20Went%20All%20Out%20To%20Keep%20Chirag%20Paswan%20On%20Board%20In%20Bihar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20Chirag%20Paswan%20versus%20his%20uncle%20Pashupati%20Paras%20in%20Bihar%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20finally%20picked%20a%20side%2C%20weeks%20before%20the%20national%20election.%20Even%20if%20it%20means%20upsetting%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20who%20has%20returned%20to%20the%20NDA%20after%20his%20latest%20alliance%20switch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20conceded%20Chirag%20Paswan's%20demand%20for%20five%20seats%2C%20including%20the%20critical%20Hajipur%20seat%20that%20elected%20his%20father%20Ram%20Vilas%20Paswan%20seven%20times%20and%20where%20his%20estranged%20uncle%20Pashupati%20Paras%20won%20in%20the%20last%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20no%20longer%20playing%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20sidekick%20in%20Bihar%2C%20has%20taken%20the%20lead%20in%20the%20NDA%20fight%20in%20the%20state.%20It%20will%20contest%2017%20of%20Bihar's%2040%20seats%2C%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20party%20will%20fight%2016%20seats%2C%20Chirag%20Paswan's%20Lok%20Janshakti%20Party%20(LJP)%20will%20contest%20five%2C%20and%20Upendra%20Kushwaha%20and%20Jitan%20Ram%20Manjhi%20will%20contest%20one%20seat%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPashupati%20Paras%2C%20who%20revolted%20against%20nephew%20Chirag%20Paswan%20and%20split%20the%20LJP%20in%202021%2C%20has%20joined%20the%20ranks%20of%20the%20BJP's%20dumped%20allies%2C%20along%20with%20Dushyant%20Chautala%20in%20Haryana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20came%20to%20pass%20after%20tough%20negotiations%20during%20which%20Chirag%20Paswan%20even%20seemed%20to%20flirt%20with%20Lalu%20Yadav's%20RJD.%20He%20claimed%20that%20the%20opposition%20ranks%20had%20offered%20him%20eight%20seats.%20In%20sticking%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20however%2C%20Chirag%20Paswan%20has%20settled%20for%20five.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Bihar%2C%20the%20major%20vote%20shares%20belong%20to%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20party%2C%20Lalu%20Yadav's%20party%2C%20and%20BJP%20-%20all%20in%20double%20digits.%20The%20Paswan%20votes%2C%20which%20make%20up%20six%20percent%20of%20the%20vote%20share%2C%20are%20mainly%20with%20Chirag%20Paswan%2C%20whose%20father%20Ram%20Vilas%20Paswan%20was%20the%20most%20influential%20leader%20of%20the%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20it%20considers%20Chirag%20Paswan%20the%20true%20political%20heir%20to%20his%20father's%20base%20-%20a%20course%20correction%20after%20it%20supported%20Pashupati%20Paras's%20move%20to%20split%20the%20party%20in%202021.%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20whose%20acrimony%20with%20Chirag%20Paswan%20is%20legendary%2C%20engineered%20the%20split%2C%20along%20with%20a%20supportive%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChirag%20Paswan%20hit%20the%20streets%20immediately%2C%20and%20within%20months%2C%20it%20was%20clear%20to%20all%2C%20including%20the%20Bihar%20BJP%2C%20that%20he%20controls%20the%20Paswan%20votes.%20So%2C%20after%20Nitish%20Kumar%20ditched%20the%20BJP%20the%20very%20next%20year%2C%20the%20BJP%20reached%20out%20to%20Chirag%20Paswan%20-%20even%20though%20his%20estranged%20uncle%20made%20it%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20cabinet%20-%20and%20ensured%20he%20campaigned%20extensively%20for%20it%20in%20every%20by-election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChirag%20Paswan%20has%20managed%20to%20hold%20his%20own%2C%20not%20bothering%20to%20make%20nice%20with%20Nitish%20Kumar%20in%20the%20weeks%20since%20his%20return%20to%20the%20NDA%20in%20January.%20Chirag%20Paswan%20has%20not%20called%20Nitish%20Kumar%20until%20now.%20Regardless%2C%20the%20BJP's%20leadership%20has%20conceded%20his%20demands%20in%20seat%20negotiations%2C%20effectively%20sinking%20Pashupati%20Paras%20and%20his%20faction.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710399300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-10%2F68s1ftj8_chirag-paswan-650_625x300_17_October_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhy-bjp-went-all-out-to-keep-chirag-paswan-on-board-in-bihar-5236150%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22When%20it%20comes%20to%20Chirag%20Paswan%20versus%20his%20uncle%20Pashupati%20Paras%20in%20Bihar%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20finally%20picked%20a%20side%2C%20weeks%20before%20the%20national%20election.%20Even%20if%20it%20means%20upsetting%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20who%20has%20returned%20to%20the%20NDA%20after%20his%20latest%20alliance%20switch.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhy-bjp-went-all-out-to-keep-chirag-paswan-on-board-in-bihar-5236150%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Uzbekistan%20Woman%20Found%20Dead%20At%20Bengaluru%20Hotel%2C%20Cops%20Suspect%20Murder%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBengaluru%20police%20are%20investigating%20the%20mysterious%20death%20of%20a%2037-year-old%20Uzbekistan%20woman%20at%20a%20hotel%20in%20the%20city.%20The%20woman%2C%20identified%20as%20Zareena%2C%20was%20found%20dead%20in%20her%20room%20at%20Jagadish%20Hotel%20in%20Bengaluru's%20Seshadripuram%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZareena%20had%20arrived%20in%20Bengaluru%20four%20days%20ago%20on%20a%20tourist%20visa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20said%20that%20the%20hotel%20staff%20knocked%20at%20Zareena's%20room%2C%20which%20is%20on%20the%20second%20floor%2C%20yesterday%20afternoon%20at%204.30%20pm.%20On%20not%20receiving%20a%20response%2C%20they%20unlocked%20the%20door%20with%20a%20master%20key%20and%20found%20her%20lying%20dead.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hotel%20manager%20promptly%20filed%20a%20complaint%2C%20and%20police%20registered%20a%20case%20of%20mysterious%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20said%20that%20an%20investigation%20is%20on%2C%20but%20prima%20facie%20evidence%20points%20to%20murder.%20They%20believe%20that%20Zareena%20was%20smothered%20and%20have%20sent%20the%20body%20to%20Bowring%20Hospital%20for%20post-mortem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Forensic%20Science%20Laboratory%20(FSL)%20team%2C%20accompanied%20by%20a%20canine%20squad%2C%20meticulously%20combed%20through%20the%20room%20for%20any%20traces%20of%20evidence%20that%20could%20unravel%20the%20mystery%20in%20the%20case.%20The%20CCTV%20and%20register%20at%20the%20hotel%20are%20being%20examined%20to%20see%20if%20anyone%20visited%20Zareena's%20room%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710399120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fb0i89l6o_uzbek-woman_625x300_14_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fuzbekistan-woman-found-dead-at-bengaluru-hotel-cops-suspect-murder-5236140%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bengaluru%20police%20are%20investigating%20the%20mysterious%20death%20of%20a%2037-year-old%20Uzbekistan%20woman%20at%