20candidate%20has%20had%20a%20political%20background%20may%20not%20be%20a%20sufficient%20reason%20in%20all%20cases%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Collegium%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Collegium%20also%20comprises%20Justices%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20and%20B.R.%20Gavai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Collegium%20also%20referenced%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-victoria-gowri-petitions%5C%22%3Econtroversial%20elevation%20of%20Lekshmana%20Chandra%20Victoria%20Gowri%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20was%20made%20a%20Madras%20high%20court%20judge%20in%202023.%20Gowri%20had%20drawn%20criticism%20for%20her%20controversial%20remarks%20against%20religious%20minorities%20and%20her%20alleged%20links%20with%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20example%2C%20in%20the%20recent%20past%2C%20an%20advocate%20has%20been%20appointed%20as%20a%20Judge%20of%20the%20High%20Court%20though%20she%20was%20an%20office%20bearer%20of%20a%20political%20party%20prior%20to%20her%20elevation%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Collegium%20said%20when%20responding%20on%20Madhavan%E2%80%99s%20elevation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMadhavan%20is%20from%20a%20Scheduled%20Caste%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710394205000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F25132016%2FSupreme-court4.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsc-collegium-rejects-govts-objections-to-judge-appointment-for-political-sympathies%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3B...the%20mere%20fact%20that%20the%20candidate%20has%20had%20a%20political%20background%20may%20not%20be%20a%20sufficient%20reason%20%5Bto%20deny%20elevation%5D%20in%20all%20cases%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Collegium%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsc-collegium-rejects-govts-objections-to-judge-appointment-for-political-sympathies%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22