0occur%20when%20someone%20(usually%20a%20government)%20intentionally%20disrupts%20the%20internet%20or%20social%20media%20networks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20measure%20has%20been%20widely%20criticised%20as%20too%20drastic%20a%20curbing%20of%20freedom%20of%20expression%20and%20an%20encroachment%20of%20peoples%E2%80%99%20everyday%20lives%2C%20especially%20if%20it%20is%20done%20to%20shut%20down%20dissent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEgypt%E2%80%99s%202011%20revolution%20and%20the%20failed%20Turkish%20military%20coup%20of%202016%20are%20prime%20examples%20of%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.statista.com%2Ftopics%2F11456%2Finternet-freedom-worldwide%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einternet%20shutdowns%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0employed%20in%20this%20way.%20In%20India%20%E2%80%93%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.statista.com%2Ftopics%2F6071%2Finternet-freedom-in-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecountry%20that%20cuts%20internet%20access%20the%20most%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20shutdowns%20have%20in%20the%20past%20clustered%20in%20Kashmir%20and%20Rajasthan%2C%20where%20they%20have%20been%20used%20during%20protests%20(and%20preemptively%20when%20protests%20were%20expected)%2C%20but%20also%20during%20exams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20ethnic%20tensions%20in%20Manipur%20state%20led%20to%20most%20targeted%20shutdowns%20employed%20by%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%202023%20Indian%20internet%20blockages%20and%20shutdowns%20affected%20around%2059%20million%20people%20for%20a%20total%20of%20almost%208%2C000%20hours%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.top10vpn.com%2Fresearch%2Fcost-of-internet-shutdowns%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20highest%20in%20the%20world%20when%20combined%20according%20to%20Top10VPN%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Ethiopia%2C%20Myanmar%20and%20Iran%2C%20the%20suppression%20of%20dissent%2C%20protest%20and%20in%20one%20instant%20the%20Orthodox%20church%2C%20have%20caused%20almost%20equally%20long%20user%20hours%20of%20internet%20blocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAcross%20the%20world%2C%20internet%20shutdowns%20and%20deliberate%20slowdowns%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.statista.com%2Fchart%2F29415%2Fglobal-internet-shutdowns-timeline%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehave%20become%20more%20common%20once%20again%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Given%20how%20important%20the%20internet%20is%20in%20everyday%20life%2C%20limiting%20access%20to%20it%20can%20have%20financial%20consequences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Russia%2C%20Ethiopia%20and%20Myanmar%2C%20the%20huge%20number%20of%20shutdowns%20and%20their%20length%20are%20getting%20very%20expensive.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.top10vpn.com%2Fresearch%2Fcost-of-internet-shutdowns%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETop10VPN%20found%20that%20around%201%2C350%20hours%20of%20intentional%20internet%20downtime%20and%20targeted%20blocks%20in%202023%20have%20cost%20the%20Russian%20economy%20%244%20billion%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13230140%2F%25E0%25B0%2585%25E0%25B0%2582%25E0%25B0%25A4%25E0%25B0%25B0%25E0%25B1%258D%25E0%25B0%259C%25E0%25B0%25BE%25E0%25B0%25B2%25E0%25B0%2582-1024x1024.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13230140%2F%25E0%25B0%2585%25E0%25B0%2582%25E0%25B0%25A4%25E0%25B0%25B0%25E0%25B1%258D%25E0%25B0%259C%25E0%25B0%25BE%25E0%25B0%25B2%25E0%25B0%2582-1024x1024.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-con