ge%20that%20his%20daily%20wages%20could%20take%20months%20to%20compensate.%20Under%20such%20circumstances%2C%20a%20pit%20%E2%80%93%20making%20access%20to%20his%20kutcha%20house%20harder%20%E2%80%93%20was%20the%20only%20way%20to%20secure%20his%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20one%20decade%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20adopted%20eight%20villages%20in%20Varanasi%20under%20the%20Sansad%20Adarsh%20Gram%20Yojana%20(SAGY).%20Chauhan%E2%80%99s%20village%20Domri%2C%20next%20to%20the%20river%20Ganga%2C%20is%20one%20of%20them.%20Under%20this%20scheme%2C%20each%20parliamentarian%20in%20India%20adopts%20one%20village%20from%20their%20constituency%20to%20make%20it%20a%20%E2%80%98model%20village%E2%80%99%20within%20their%20tenure.%20Modi%20announced%20the%20SAGY%20in%20his%20first%20Independence%20Day%20speech%20in%202014%2C%20with%20promises%20of%20smart%20schools%2C%20universal%20access%20to%20basic%20health%20facilities%20and%20%3Cem%3Epukka%3C%2Fem%3E%20housing%20for%20homeless%20villagers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13131505%2FSJ1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22904%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13131505%2FSJ1.jpg%20904w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13131505%2FSJ1-300x224.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-701441%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22676%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EMahesh%20Chauhan%20digging%20a%20pit%20in%20front%20of%20his%20house.%20Photo%3A%20Srishti%20Jaswal%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Domri%20is%20far%20from%20being%20a%20model%20village.%20In%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20house%2C%20most%20families%20in%20the%20Harijan%20Basti%20say%20they%20survive%20the%20monsoons%20under%20plastic%20and%20use%20a%20thin%20cloth%20for%20protection%20from%20mosquitoes%20when%20sleeping%20outside.%20For%20many%2C%20the%20cold%20becomes%20more%20unbearable%20than%20summer%20and%20rain.%20But%20the%20lack%20of%20housing%20worst%20hit%20Chauhan%20when%20his%20goats%20were%20recently%20stolen.%20He%20asked%2C%20%E2%80%9CCould%20my%20goats%20have%20been%20stolen%20if%20I%20had%20a%20house%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20announcing%20the%20SAGY%20in%202014%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20in%20its%202019%20manifesto%20seeking%20a%20second%20term%20had%20promised%20%E2%80%98gram%20swaraj%E2%80%99%20with%20Saashray%20(pukka%20houses%20for%20all%20living%20in%20kutcha%20houses)%20by%202022%2C%20Sujal%20(tap%20water%20for%20all)%20by%202024%2C%20Suchna%20se%20Sashaktikaran%20(digital%20connectivity%20through%20Bharatnet%20for%20all%20panchayats)%20by%202022%2C%20Sadak%20se%20Samriddhi%20(massive%20road%20connectivity)%20and%20Swachata%20se%20Sampannata%20(100%20%25%20disposal%20of%20liquid%20wastewater).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20552px)%2085vw%2C%20552px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13131708%2FSJ3.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22552%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13131708%2FSJ3.png%20552w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13131708%2FSJ3-212x300.png%20212w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-701443%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22782%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPage%2016%20from%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%E2%80%99s%202019%20manifesto%20which%20promises%20Gram%20Swaraj.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fem%3E%20reporting%20found%20that%20in%20most%20of%20the%20villages%20adopted%20by%20Modi%20in%20Varanasi%2C%20the%20%E