04%2FSJ4.jpg%20904w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13131804%2FSJ4-300x224.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-701444%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22676%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20woman%20washing%20utensils%20with%20stale%20water%20in%20Parampur%20village.%20Photo%3A%20Srishti%20Jaswal%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHimanshu%2C%20an%20associate%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jnu.ac.in%2Fcontent%2Fhimanshu2%5C%22%3E%20professor%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%20(JNU)%E2%80%99s%20Centre%20for%20Economic%20Studies%20and%20Planning%20said%20there%20are%20many%20issues%20in%20the%20design%20of%20policies.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20subsidies%20given%20for%20these%20policies%20are%20hardly%20enough%20and%20local%20corruption%20makes%20it%20even%20more%20difficult%20to%20make%20a%20change%20on%20ground.%20The%20toilet%20is%20a%20good%20example.%20They%20are%20bound%20to%20be%20non-functional%20because%20with%20such%20little%20money%2C%20hardly%20any%20good%20toilets%20can%20be%20made.%20Similarly%20in%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Awas%20Yojana%2C%20the%20subsidy%20is%20not%20sufficient%20to%20be%20able%20to%20build%20a%20proper%20house.%20Then%20there%20is%20convergence%20between%20various%20programmes%2C%20for%20instance%20people%20are%20given%20a%20toilet%20without%20housing%20or%20people%20are%20given%20housing%20without%20tap%20water.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20406px)%2085vw%2C%20406px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13134054%2FIMG_2860.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22BJP%20promises%20performance%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22406%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13134054%2FIMG_2860.jpg%20874w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13134054%2FIMG_2860-219x300.jpg%20219w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire