2%20height%3D%5C%22610%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EWomen%20in%20Parampur%20village%20say%20water%20is%20a%20big%20issue%20for%20them.%20They%20have%20taps%20but%20those%20taps%20have%20no%20water.%20Photo%3A%20Srishti%20Jaswal%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDigital%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSuchna%20se%20Sashaktikaran%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20promise%20to%20bring%20digital%20connectivity%20to%20all%20panchayats%20in%20India%20by%202022%20is%20also%20lagging%20after%20missing%20multiple%20deadlines.%20Out%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%202.5%20lakh%20gram%20panchayats%2C%20around%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbbnl.nic.in%2F%5C%22%3E2%20lakh%20gram%3C%2Fa%3E%20panchayats%20have%20been%20connected%20through%20BharatNet.%20However%2C%20this%20does%20not%20mean%20that%20these%20gram%20panchayats%20have%20functioning%20internet.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbbnl.nic.in%2F%5C%22%3EOnly%206%2C307%20panchayats%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20active%20Wi-Fi%20as%20per%20Bharat%20Broadband%20Network%20Limited%20data%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20240129084126%2Fhttps%3A%2Fbbnl.nic.in%2F%5C%22%3EJanuary%2029%2C%202024.%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20not%20able%20to%20verify%20how%20many%20villages%20adopted%20by%20Modi%20were%20connected%20with%20the%20internet%20as%20most%20of%20the%20gram%20panchayat%20offices%20were%20closed%2C%20and%20the%20BBNL%20data%20does%20not%20reveal%20the%20names%20of%20the%20connected%20panchayats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERoads%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20promise%20of%20robust%20road%20connectivity%2C%20many%20villages%20adopted%20by%20Modi%20do%20not%20have%20functional%20roads.%20The%20road%20in%20Nagepur%20village%2C%20outside%20Rajnath%20and%20Sushila%E2%80%99s%20kutcha%20house%2C%20is%20completely%20broken.%20Since%20there%20is%20no%20drainage%20or%20sewerage%20lines%2C%20the%20dirty%20water%20flows%20through%20the%20gully%20and%20often%20gets%20trapped%20in%20potholes.%20The%20couple%2C%20in%20their%2060s%2C%20have%20now%20led%20their%20entire%20lives%20without%20roofs.%20They%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20who%20do%20not%20have%20a%20roof%20do%20not%20care%20about%20the%20roads.%E2%80%9D%20Their%20daughter-in-law%2C%2028-year-old%20Karma%20Devi%2C%20asked%20if%20they%20will%20ever%20get%20a%20better%20standard%20of%20living%2C%20especially%20since%20her%20husband%20is%20often%20unemployed.%20She%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CHe%20works%20for%20two%20days%2C%20then%20sits%20at%20home%20for%20the%20next%20two%20days.%E2%80%9D%20While%20cuddling%20her%20newborn%2C%20she%20pointed%20towards%20a%20pothole-filled%20route%20and%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CRoad%E2%80%A6this%20is%20what%20it%20is%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20429px)%2085vw%2C%20429px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13132906%2FSJ13.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22429%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13132906%2FSJ13.jpg%20901w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13132906%2FSJ13-225x300.jpg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13132906%2FSJ13-769x1024.jpg%20769w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-701452%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22571%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20road%20in%20Nagepur%20village%20outside%20Rajnath%20and%20Sushila%E2%80%99s%20kutcha%20house.%20Photo%3A%20Srishti%20Jaswal%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAzhar%20Ansari%20from%20Pure%20village%20claimed%20that%20when%20Modi%20adopted%20their%20village%20a%20road%20widening%20programme%20was%20sanctioned.%20He%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20road%20was%20supposed%20to%20get%20longer%20and%20wider.%20It%20has%20not%20happened%20yet.%20At%20least%20the%20tasks%20that%20they%20have%20taken%2C%20they%20should%20be%20fulfilled.%20Else%20an%20inquiry%20should%20be%20set%20up.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELakhandar%20Ram%2C%20an%20elderly%20Dalit%20man%20and%20community%20leader%2C%20equated%20their%20village%20with%20hell%20and%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20no%20facilities%20here.%20I%20do%20not%20know%20how%20a%20drain%20was%20sanctioned%20a%20couple%20of%20years%20back.%20Otherwise%20every%20morning%20commuters%20abused%20us%20(because%20of%20overflowing%20liquid%20waste%20water).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20construction%20of%20rural%20roads%20in%20India%20has%20taken%20a%20backseat%20from%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20years.%20The%20annual%20target%20of%2047%2C171%20kilometres%20of%20rural%20roads%20construction%20under%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Gram%20Sadak%20Yojana%2C%20was%20missed%20by%2017%2C414%20kilometres%20in%202023.%20The%20government%20was%20only%20able%20to%20connect%20nearly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fomms.nic.in%2F%5C%22%3E617%20hamlets%20with%20roads%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20situation%20was%20similar%20in%202022%20when%20nearly%207%2C991%20kilometres%20of%20road%20sanctioned%20was%20not%20constructed.%20A%20year%20before%20that%20the%20target%20was%20missed%20by%209%2C487%20kilometres.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESujit%20Kumar%20Patel%2C%20who%20was%20pradhan%20of%20Kakrahiya%20villlage%20when%20Modi%20adopted%20it%2C%20claimed%20the%20village%20got%20a%20road%20and%20water%20during%20the%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20government%20in%20UP.%20He%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CUnder%20the%20Lohiya%20Yojana%20of%20the%20Akhilesh%20government%2C%20we%20got%208-10%20aawas%2C%20for%20each%20awas%203.25%20lacs%20were%20sanctioned.%20We%20also%20got%20a%20road%20made.%E2%80%9D%20He%20claimed%20Kakrahiya%20village%20is%20one%20of%20the%20best%20in%20the%20region%20because%20people%20are%20very%20%E2%80%9Cactive%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20what%20was%20done%20under%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20tenure%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CModi%20also%20did%20very%20good%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20but%20was%20unable%20to%20recount%20Gram%20Swaraj%20developments%20as%20promised%20by%20the%20prime%20minister.%20He%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CLook%2C%20we%20have%2024%C3%977%20electricity%20%2C%20crime%20is%20almost%20over%2C%20roads%20are%20also%20very%20good.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESanitation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20villager%2C%20Lakhandar%2C%20claimed%20the%20situation%20of%20toilets%20in%20their%20village%20is%20no%20good.%20He%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CEvery%20morning%20we%20fight%20and%20abuse%20each%20other%20to%20urinate.%E2%80%9D%20Ansari%2C%20his%20neighbour%20from%20Pure%20village%2C%20showed%20how%20the%20public%20toilets%20in%20their%20village%20have%20no%20water%20and%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20Modi%20ji%20has%20adopted%20our%20village%2C%20they%20should%20send%20someone%20to%20see%20what%20facilities%20are%20here%20and%20what%20facilities%20are%20missing.%20It%20is%20his%20responsibility.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Jayapur%20village%2C%20in%20the%20toilet%20assigned%20to%20Lal%20Dhar%2C%20the%20door%20is%20half%20collapsed%20and%20the%20pit%20is%20almost%20full.%20Nearly%2010%20people%20use%20that%20toilet%20which%20has%20no%20tap.%20The%20women%20of%20Lal%20Dhar%E2%80%99s%20household%20are%20only%20able%20to%20use%20the%20toilet%20at%20night.%C2%A0%20He%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20village.%20What%20happened%20was%20that%20they%20did%20some%20fake%20work%20and%20went%20away.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fswachhbharatmission.gov.in%2Fsbmcms%2Fwritereaddata%2Fimages%2Fpdf%2FGuidelines%2FComplete-set-guidelines.pdf%5C%22%3E%20Swachh%20Bharat%20Mission%20guidelines%20released%20in%202017%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9Ca%20duly%20completed%20household%20sanitary%20latrine%20unit%20shall%20comprise%20of%20a%20sanitary%20substructure%20that%20safely%20confines%20human%20faeces%20and%20eliminates%20the%20need%20for%20human%20handling%20before%20it%20is%20fully%20decomposed%20or%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwedc-knowledge.lboro.ac.uk%2Fresources%2Fbooklets%2FG028-Latrine-superstructures-on-line.pdf%5C%22%3Esuperstructure%20with%20water%20facility%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20a%20hand%20wash%20unit%20for%20cleaning%20and%20handwashing.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20almost%20all%20villages%20that%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20toured%20in%20Varanasi%2C%20many%20toilets%20were%20completely%20abandoned%20as%20they%20had%20no%20roofs%20or%20their%20pits%20were%20full%2C%20making%20them%20useless.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13133126%2FSJ14.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22904%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13133126%2FSJ14.jpg%20904w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13133126%2FSJ14-300x224.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-701453%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22676%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20toilet%E2%80%99s%20pit%20is%20full%2C%20making%20it%20unusable%20for%20villagers%20in%20Parampur.%20Photo%3A%20Srishti%20Jaswal%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESrinarayan%20Singh%20Patel%2C%20who%20was%20the%20%3Cem%3Epradhan%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20Jayapur%20when%20the%20village%20was%20adopted%20by%20Modi%2C%20claimed%20a%20lot%20has%20been%20done%2C%20such%20as%20the%20opening%20of%20two%20banks%20and%20a%20post%20office.%20When%20asked%20about%20the%20condition%20of%20the%20Harijan%20Basti%20in%20his%20village%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThose%20who%20are%20remaining%2C%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20mean%20they%20will%20not%20get%20it%20(housing).%E2%80%9D%20Regarding%20the%20broken%20toilets%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThose%20who%20have%20got%20it%20(toilets)%20before%2C%20upkeep%20is%20their%20responsibility%2C%20not%20the%20government%E2%80%99s.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20he%20also%20claimed%20that%20the%20Panchayat%20office%20has%20internet%2C%20he%20said%20the%20work%20is%20slow%20because%20the%20complete%20money%20has%20not%20been%20sanctioned%20yet.%20He%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CSlowly%2C%20slowly%20the%20work%20is%20happening%20because%20after%20the%20BJP%20government%20came%2C%20these%20new%20schemes%20have%20come%20up.%20But%20it%20will%20take%20time.%20After%20complete%20funding%20is%20received%2C%20complete%20work%20will%20be%20done.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESegregation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20villages%20that%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fem%3Evisited%20were%20segregated%20based%20on%20caste%20and%20religion.%20In%20most%20villages%2C%20Muslims%20were%20rarely%20present.%20In%20Pure%20Gaon%2C%20where%20there%20is%20a%20Muslim%20population%2C%20there%20were%20separate%20areas%20for%20upper%20castes%2C%20Dalits%2C%20Yadavs%20and%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHimanshu%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20feature%20of%20segregation%20is%20unlikely%20to%20go%20away%20because%20they%20are%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20villages.%20Caste-related%20issues%20will%20remain.%20The%20lack%20of%20access%20is%20determined%20by%20local%20power%20structures.%20As%20in%20any%20other%20village%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20those%20will%20remain.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20level%20of%20deficit%20is%20very%20high%2C%20it%20is%20not%20going%20to%20be%20covered%20in%20one%20year%20or%20even%20ten%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20however%2C%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9CHolding%20the%20government%20accountable%20is%20a%20job%20that%20democracy%20must%20do.%20Political%20parties%20must%20be%20questioned%20on%20these%20promises%20and%20they%20must%20be%20held%20accountable%20for%20not%20fulfilling%20whatever%20promises%20they%20made.%20That%20is%20supposed%20to%20be%20the%20job%20of%20the%20electorate.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710379844000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13131601%2FSJ2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fpromised-gram-swaraj-eludes-varanasi-villages-narendra-modi-adopted%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20promises%20of%20housing%20for%20all%2C%20working%20toilets%20and%20connectivity%20remain%20unfulfilled%20even%20in%20the%20villages%20the%20prime%20minister%20took%20on%20as%20his%20own.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fpromised-gram-swaraj-eludes-varanasi-villages-narendra-modi-adopted%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98The%20Masked%20Singer%E2%80%99%20Reveals%20Identity%20of%20Afghan%20Hound%3A%20Here%20Is%20the%20Celebrity%20Under%20the%20Costume%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710378000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FMS-1104_Show_00449_f-e1710360443698.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235941068%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22SPOILER%20ALERT%3A%20Do%20not%20read%20ahead%20if%20you%20have%20not%20watched%20Season%2011%2C%20Episode%202%20of%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Masked%20Singer%2C%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Wizard%20of%20Oz%20Night%2C%E2%80%9D%20which%20aired%20March%2013%20on%20Fox.%20Chrisley%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20best%2C%20at%20least%20on%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Masked%20Singer.%E2%80%9D%20As%20her%20%E2%80%9CChrisley%20Knows%20Best%E2%80%9D%20parents%20Julie%20and%20Todd%20Chrisley%20remain%20in%20prison%20for%20bank%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Varietyschneider%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fthe-masked-singer-season-11-epi