ing%20two%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20north-eastern%20states%2C%20citing%20concerns%20that%20it%20could%20undermine%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20ongoing%20discussions%20with%20China.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20foreign%20ministries%20of%20India%20and%20Bhutan%20announced%20Tobgay%E2%80%99s%20visit%2C%20which%20will%20be%20from%20March%2014%20to%2018.%20This%20will%20be%20his%20first%20overseas%20visit%20after%20winning%20a%20second%20term%20in%20the%20general%20elections%20in%20January.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mea.gov.in%2Fpress-releases.htm%3Fdtl%2F37703%2FOfficial%2BVisit%2Bof%2BPrime%2BMinister%2Bof%2BBhutan%2Bto%2BIndia%2BMarch%2B1418%2B2024%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20visit%20would%20%E2%80%9Cprovide%20an%20opportunity%20to%20the%20two%20sides%20to%20review%20the%20progress%20in%20our%20unique%20partnership%20and%20to%20discuss%20ways%20and%20means%20to%20expand%20the%20enduring%20ties%20of%20friendship%20and%20cooperation%20between%20India%20and%20Bhutan%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mfa.gov.bt%2Fofficial-visit-of-prime-minister-dasho-tshering-tobgay-to-india%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Bhutanese%20foreign%20ministry%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20claimed%20that%20the%20visit%20would%20%E2%80%9Cfurther%20strengthen%20the%20close%20ties%20of%20friendship%20and%20cooperation%20that%20exists%20between%20the%20two%20countries%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20has%20learnt%20that%20India%20had%20proposed%20to%20connect%20Tawang%20in%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20to%20Guwahati%20in%20Assam%20with%20a%20motorable%20road%20through%20Bhutan.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A