military%20infrastructure%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20the%20end%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20there%20has%20been%20notable%20momentum%20in%20Bhutan%20towards%20the%20finalisation%20of%20its%20border%20negotiations%20with%20China.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20informed%20observers%2C%20Thimpu%E2%80%99s%20proactive%20stance%20is%20driven%20by%20the%20acknowledgment%20that%20China%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2Fdiplomacy%2Farticle%2F3251394%2Fchinese-village-construction-disputed-zone-outpaces-china-bhutan-border-talks%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esalami%20slicing%E2%80%99%20tactics%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20along%20the%20border%20cannot%20be%20effectively%20halted%20due%20to%20Bhutan%E2%80%99s%20lack%20of%20resources.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20October%202021%2C%20Bhutan%20and%20China%20signed%20a%20memorandum%20of%20understanding%20to%20expedite%20boundary%20talks%20with%20a%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkuenselonline.com%2Fbhutan-china-sign-mou-to-expedite-boundary-negotiations%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethree%20stage%20roadmap%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D.%20After%20the%20delimitation%20of%20the%20border%20on%20maps%2C%20it%20envisages%20joint%20surveys%20for%20demarcating%20the%20border.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%2025%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20round%20of%20boundary%20talks%20in%20October%20last%20year%2C%20the%20two%20sides%20agreed%20on%20the%20guidelines%20of%20the%20joint%20technical%20team%20that%20would%20delimit%20and%20demarcate%20the%20boundary.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20a%20meeting%20with%20Bhutan%E2%80%99s%20foreign%20minister%2C%20Chinese%20foreign%20minister%20Wang%20Yi%20said%20that%20Beijing%20was%20ready%20to%20conclude%20the%20process%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fchina-bhutan-vow-to-conclude-border-talks-soon-will-have-implications-for-india%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eas%20soon%20as%20possible%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBhutan%E2%80%99s%20reluctance%20to%20authorise%20the%20Indian%20military%20road%20until%20the%20border%20with%20China%20is%20conclusively%20settled%20suggests%20that%20Thimphu%20is%20equally%20eager%20to%20conclude%20the%20matter%20without%20jeopardising%20the%20ongoing%20boundary%20negotiations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710354838000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F10134907%2F24309575841_545d70a37a_k.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fbhutan-pm-india-vist-china-border-talks-shadow%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20has%20proposed%20connecting%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20and%20Assam%20with%20a%20motorable%20road%20through%20Bhutan.%20But%20it%20is%20understood%20that%20Bhutan's%20government%20is%20not%20keen%20on%20the%20proposal%20until%20its%20border%20with%20China%20is%20demarcated.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fbhutan-pm-india-vist-china-border-talks-shadow%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20is%20About%20Truth%2C%20the%20Environment%20and%20Democracy%2C%20Says%20Sonam%20Wangchuk%20on%20Day%208%20of%20His%20Climate%20Fast%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13231912%2FWangchuk-Sonam.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3EClimate%20activist%20and%20innovator%20Sonam%20Wangchuk%20is%20on%20a%20%E2%80%98climate%20fast%E2%80%99%20at%20Leh%20in%20Ladakh.%20The%20Ramon%20Magsaysay%20Award%20winner%20of%202017%20is%20on%20a%20hunger%20