le%20across%20the%20country%20to%20join%20him%20on%20one%20day%20of%20his%2021-day%20fast%3A%20on%20Sunday%20(March%2017).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20citizens%20are%20responding%3A%20many%20plan%20to%20come%20together%20in%20silent%20gatherings%20to%20take%20the%20fast%20on%20Sunday%20and%20show%20solidarity%20with%20Ladakh%2C%20its%20people%20and%20its%20environment.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CAbout%20truth%2C%20environment%2C%20democracy%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%20virtual%20press%20conference%20conducted%20by%20the%20environmental%20group%20Friends%20of%20Ladakh%20and%20Friends%20of%20Nature%20(FOLFON%2C%20which%20has%20been%20banded%20together%20to%20spread%20the%20word%20of%20Wangchuk%E2%80%99s%20climate%20fast)%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20Wangchuk%20first%20gave%20an%20introduction%20to%20his%20ongoing%2021-day%20climate%20fast%20at%20Leh%20in%20Ladakh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EToday%20is%20day%20eight%20of%20his%20fast%20and%20he%20is%20surviving%20only%20on%20water%20and%20salt%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FSAVELADAKH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23SAVELADAKH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FSAVEHIMALAYAS%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23SAVEHIMALAYAS%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnSonam%20Wangchuk%20appeals%20to%20the%20world%20to%20live%20simply%2C%3Cbr%3E%5Cnstarts%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FClimateFast%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23ClimateFast%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%2021%20days%20(extendable%20till%20death)%3Cbr%3E%5CnPlease%20watch%20full%20video%20in%20English%20here%3A%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FXHkcIdQQ7b%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FXHkcIdQQ7b%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca