mmu%20and%20Kashmir%20for%20some%2070%20years%2C%20its%20people%20have%20always%20wanted%20to%20be%20an%20entity%20of%20their%20own%2C%20because%20it%20had%20always%20been%20an%20independent%20kingdom%20in%20the%20Himalayas%20like%20Sikkim%2C%20Bhutan%20and%20Tibet%2C%20said%20Wangchuk.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20because%20Ladakh%E2%80%99s%20topography%2C%20environment%2C%20culture%20and%20linguistics%20have%20all%20been%20very%20different%20not%20just%20from%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%20India%2C%20but%20the%20world%20too.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20Ladakh%20received%20the%20tag%20of%20a%20Union%20territory%20(UT)%20in%202019%20(%E2%80%9Cmuch%20to%20all%20our%20surprise%E2%80%9D%2C%20in%20Wangchuk%E2%80%99s%20words)%2C%20the%20people%20of%20Ladakh%20were%20very%20grateful%20to%20the%20ruling%20party.%20But%20their%20%E2%80%9Cexpectation%20and%20demand%E2%80%9D%20had%20always%20been%20that%20they%20have%20a%20legislative%20assembly%2C%20%E2%80%9Cwhich%20means%20the%20democratic%20representation%20of%20people%20in%20an%20assembly%20which%20will%20then%20make%20laws%20and%20policies%20to%20manage%20the%20fragile%20ecosystems%20of%20these%20mountains%E2%80%9D%2C%20Wangchuk%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20thing%20was%20about%20the%20safeguards%20of%20this%20especially%20fragile%20zone%2C%20and%20Article%20370%20provided%20that%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20we%20were%20okay%20with%20%5BArticle%5D%20370%20going%20because%20only%20that%20could%20allow%20Ladakh%20to%20be%20a%20separate%20entity.%20We%20were%20okay%20about%20that%20for%20Ladakh%20%E2%80%A6%20of%20course%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20different%20case%20for%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98%E2%80%9CNatural%20no-brainer%E2%80%9D%20but%20BJP%20didn%E2%80%99t%20deliver%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELadakh%20expected%20that%20its%20safeguards%20would%20come%20from%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%2C%20the%20climate%20activist%20said%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBecause%20this%20%5Bschedule%5D%20is%20tailor-made%20for%20hilly%20regions%20with%20distinct%20indigenous%20tribal%20communities.%20And%20normally%2C%2050%25%20tribal%20population%20is%20enough%20to%20qualify%20for%20that%2C%20but%20Ladakh%20has%2097%25.%20So%20we%20were%20hands-down%20qualified%20for%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20commented.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20we%20had%20no%20doubt%20that%20the%20government%20that%20was%20kind%20enough%20to%20make%20Ladakh%20a%20UT%20would%20also%20give%20us%20that.%20It%20was%20a%20natural%20no-brainer.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20government%20itself%20assured%20the%20people%20of%20Ladakh%20again%20and%20again%20that%20this%20safeguard%20would%20be%20given%20to%20Ladakh%2C%20and%20they%20spoke%20in%20large%20gatherings%20about%20this%2C%20Wangchuk%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-roots-of-discontent-in-ladakh%5C%22%3EThe%20Roots%20of%20Discontent%20in%20Ladakh%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20government%20even%20kept%20it%20in%20its%202019%20election%20manifesto%20%E2%80%93%20it%20was%20in%20fact%20one%20of%20the%20top%20three%20promises%20they%20made.%20(Behind%20Wangchuk%E2%80%99s%20seat%20hung%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20manifesto%20in%20which%20the%20BJP%20promised%20to%20implement%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%2C%20and%20the%20climate%20activist%20also%20pointed%20to%20it%20in%20between%20his%20address).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20people%20voted%20%E2%80%9Cheavily%E2%80%9D%20for%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20party%20won%20from%20Ladakh.%20But%20the%20BJP%20didn%E2%80%99t%20keep%20their%20promise%2C%20Wangchuk%20said.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20months%2C%20they%20went%20silent.%20They%20were%20even%20upset%20when%20we%20reminded%20them%20of%20this%20promise.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWangchuk%20also%20alleged%20that%20the%20government%20even%20took%20police%20action%20against%20anybody%20who%20uttered%20the%20words%20%E2%80%9CSixth%20Schedule%E2%80%9D%2C%20despite%20it%20being%20a%20provision%20in%20the%20Indian%20constitution.%20So%20in%202020%2C%20Ladakhis%20decided%20to%20boycott%20the%20elections%20to%20the%20Hill%20Council%20of%20Leh%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20the%20present%20government%20sent%20a%20special%20airplane%20to%20Leh%2C%20took%20Ladakhi%20leaders%20to%20Delhi%20and%20appealed%20to%20them%20to%20let%20the%20election%20proceed.%20The%20government%20promised%20they%20would%20%E2%80%9Csolve%20everything%E2%80%9D%20after%20the%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COur%20tribal%20indigenous%20leaders%20and%20people%20are%20very%20trusting%2C%E2%80%9D%20Wangchuk%20said.%20So%20once%20again%2C%20the%20people%20of%20Ladakh%20%E2%80%9Cvoted%20heavily%E2%80%9D%20for%20the%20BJP%20and%20they%20formed%20the%20government%20for%20the%20Ladakh%20Autonomous%20Hill%20Council.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETwo%20elections%20were%20thus%20won%20on%20this%20promise%20by%20the%20BJP%2C%20Wangchuk%20pointed%20out.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYet%20four%20years%20later%2C%20nothing%20has%20happened%2C%20he%20added.%20The%20home%20ministry%20kept%20%E2%80%9Cdilly-dallying%E2%80%9D%2C%20not%20taking%20decisions%2C%20giving%20several%20excuses%2C%20and%20so%20on%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Climate%20fast%20is%20now%20our%20only%20resort%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CFinally%20on%20March%204%2C%20they%20outright%20denied%20any%20possibility%20%5Bof%20this%5D%20and%20said%20that%20we%20cannot%20give%20you%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%2C%E2%80%9D%20Wangchuk%20said.%20A%20UT%20with%20legislature%20or%20statehood%20is%20also%20not%20possible%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELadakhi%20people%2C%20therefore%2C%20%E2%80%9Care%20very%20hurt%E2%80%9D%20and%20our%20%E2%80%9Conly%20resort%E2%80%9D%20is%20to%20start%20a%20movement%2C%20Wangchuk%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20that%20not%20only%20people%20in%20Ladakh%20but%20all%20over%20the%20nation%20join%20us%20in%20the%20support%20and%20defence%20of%20truth%20and%20justice%20%E2%80%A6%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20about%20Ladakh.%20When%20somebody%20makes%20a%20promise%2C%20they%20must%20keep%20it%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20like%20giving%20a%20cheque%20which%20says%20Sixth%20Schedule%20and%20then%20you%20take%20it%20and%20it%20bounces.%20That%20should%20not%20be%20acceptable.%20In%20fact%2C%20it%20should%20be%20punishable.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20we%20are%20on%20a%20fast.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F03180459%2Fimage-1809.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221007%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F03180459%2Fimage-1809.png%201007w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F03180459%2Fimage-1809-300x130.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-695567%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22435%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThousands%20of%20protesters%20rallied%20in%20Leh%20and%20Kargil%20districts%20of%20Ladakh%20on%20Saturday%2C%20February%203%2C%20in%20protest%20against%20the%20constitutional%20changes%20brought%20about%20by%20the%20reading%20down%20of%20Article%20370.%20Photo%3A%20By%20Special%20Arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMore%20and%20more%20people%20are%20joining%20the%20fast%20in%20different%20days%2C%20Wangchuk%20said%2C%20showing%20a%20glimpse%20of%20the%20people%20gathered%20at%20the%20site%20sitting%20with%20him%20via%20his%20phone%20camera.%20Around%201%2C000%20people%20have%20joined%20him%20for%20the%20fast%20on%20March%2013%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20resentment%20among%20people%2C%20but%20we%20hope%20that%20this%20shows%20the%20central%20%5BUnion%5D%20government%20how%20serious%20the%20matter%20is%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20struggle%20will%20take%20long%2C%20but%20we%20are%20ready%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20also%20commented%20later%2C%20in%20reply%20to%20other%20questions%20posed%20by%20activists%20and%20members%20of%20the%20media%20during%20the%20virtual%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWangchuk%20also%20said%20that%20he%20was%20%E2%80%9Csurprised%E2%80%9D%20that%20the%20government%20is%20not%20paying%20attention%20to%20their%20protest%20in%20such%20a%20sensitive%20region%2C%20which%20is%20surrounded%20by%20international%20borders.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELadakhis%20have%20supported%20the%20Indian%20army%2C%20shoulder-to-shoulder%2C%20on%20every%20occasion%20across%20decades%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20%5Bthe%20government%5D%20will%20lose%20a%20great%20friend%20if%20they%20keep%20treating%20Ladakh%20this%20way%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBecause%20Ladakhis%20will%20no%20longer%20be%20passionate%20about%20risking%20our%20lives%20to%20help%2C%20if%20they%20feel%20that%20the%20government%20is%20not%20protecting%20them%20in%20any%20way.%20It%20would%20be%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ebadkismati%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%5Bbad%20luck%5D%20if%20that%20happens.%20And%20the%20current%20ruling%20party%20will%20be%20responsible%20for%20this%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CLadakhis%20have%20always%20been%20with%20the%20country%20but%20if%20this%20continues%2C%20people%20will%20be%20very%20confused%20about%20what%20to%20do.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20it%20is%20important%20that%20the%20government%20not%20take%20this%20lightly.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20regions%2C%20religions%20and%20political%20parties%20in%20Ladakh%20are%20with%20this%20movement%3B%20even%20the%20BJP%20was%2C%20because%20they%20did%20include%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%20in%20their%20manifesto.%20But%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20different%20matter%20that%20now%20they%20are%20not%2C%20Wangchuk%20said%20in%20response%20to%20questions%20by%20other%20media%20houses.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWangchuk%20called%20on%20people%20from%20across%20India%20to%20join%20this%20%E2%80%9Cstruggle%20for%20truth%2C%20struggle%20for%20protection%20of%20fragile%20environment%20and%20struggle%20for%20democracy%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20innovator%20who%20won%20laurels%20for%20his%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fsci-tech%2Fenergy-and-environment%2Fthe-ice-stupa-man%2Farticle21250832.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eice%20stupas%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%93%20enormous%20%E2%80%98stupas%E2%80%99%20or%20blocks%20of%20ice%20constructed%20in%20such%20a%20way%20that%20it%20melts%20slower%20than%20usual%20and%20supplies%20villages%20in%20Ladakh%20with%20a%20constant%20water%20supply%20%E2%80%93%20has%20called%20on%20people%20across%20the%20country%20to%20join%20him%20on%20his%20climate%20fast%20for%20a%20single%20day%20%E2%80%93%20on%20Sunday%20(March%2017)%20%E2%80%93%20to%20show%20their%20solidarity%20and%20support%20for%20the%20movement.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20activists%20and%20environmentalists%20across%20the%20country%20are%20responding.%20People%20and%20organizations%20across%20several%20cities%20and%20towns%20in%20India%20have%20formed%20groups%20in%20solidarity%20with%20Wangchuk%E2%80%99s%20climate%20fast%2C%20and%20have%20pledged%20to%20fast%20on%20March%2017%20to%20show%20support%20for%20Ladakh%20and%20its%20environment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFOLFON%20founder%20Dilip%20Jain%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20his%20organisation%20has%2020%20active%20chapters.%20These%20include%20activists%20and%20groups%20across%20several%20states%20including%20Uttarakhand%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Punjab%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh%3B%20and%20city%20chapters%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20Kolhapur%2C%20Pune%20and%20Nagpur%20in%20Maharashtra%3B%20Coimbatore%20and%20Chennai%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%3B%20Bengaluru%20in%20Karnataka%20and%20Hyderabad%20in%20Telangana.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13232605%2FTso-Moriri-1024x600.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13232605%2FTso-Moriri-1024x600.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13232605%2FTso-Moriri-425x250.jpg%20425w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-701524%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22492%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPictured%20here%20is%20the%20Tso%20Moriri%20lake%2C%20which%20is%20part%20of%20what%20Wangchuk%20calls%20one%20of%20Ladakh%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cfragile%20ecosystems%E2%80%9D.%20Photo%3A%20Tanay%20Kibe%2FWikimedia%20Commons.%20CC%20BY-SA%202.0%20Generic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlmost%20200%20students%20from%20Ladakh%20University%20%E2%80%93%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Ladakh%20Students%E2%80%99%20Union%20%E2%80%93%20also%20joined%20Wangchuk%20on%20his%20climate%20fast%20a%20day%20ago%2C%20as%20per%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fsi%3DTYIQXB5CcYbjhs_Q%26v%3D0-pHAjV1CIM%26feature%3Dyoutu.be%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereports%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20though%20there%20were%20some%20obstacles%20that%20university%20administrators%20put%20in%20place%20to%20prevent%20their%20support%2C%20the%20students%20still%20made%20it%20to%20the%20protest%20site%20and%20will%20continue%20to%20support%20this%20movement%2C%20a%20student%20said%20in%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fsi%3DTYIQXB5CcYbjhs_Q%26v%3D0-pHAjV1CIM%26feature%3Dyoutu.be%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EYouTube%20video%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Locals%20have%20to%20manage%20Ladakh%E2%80%99s%20fragile%20ecosystems%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELadakh%20is%20home%20to%20%E2%80%9Cvery%20fragile%20ecosystems%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20from%20the%20Tso%20Moriri%20lake%20ecosystem%20to%20the%20Pangong%20ecosystem%20%E2%80%93%20or%20fragile%20cultures%20such%20as%20the%20Changpa%20tribes%2C%C2%A0%20Wangchuk%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20can%E2%80%99t%20have%20bulls%20in%20this%20China%20shop%20%E2%80%A6%20If%20it%20is%20just%20like%20this%2C%20then%20it%20is%20open%20to%20all%20industrial%20lobbies%20%5Band%5D%20mining%20lobbies%20to%20come%20and%20exploit%20this%2C%20blindly%2C%20blatantly%2C%20like%20it%20has%20happened%20in%20many%20parts%20of%20the%20Himalayas.%20And%20we%20can%20see%20the%20impacts%20of%20that%2C%20from%20Himachal%20to%20Uttarakhand%20to%20Sikkim.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20this%20to%20be%20repeated%20in%20Ladakh.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMoreover%2C%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%20is%20not%20%E2%80%9Clike%20putting%20a%20wall%20around%20Ladakh%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSometimes%20people%20say%20there%20will%20be%20no%20development%2C%20you%20want%20industries%20for%20jobs%20and%20so%20on.%20Jobs%20and%20industries%20can%20still%20come%3B%20but%20only%20with%20consultations%20with%20the%20local%20and%20indigenous%20people.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20all%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%20does%20is%20it%20forms%20autonomous%20councils%2C%20like%20microassemblies%2C%20where%20indigenous%20people%20send%20their%20chosen%20elected%20representatives.%20And%20they%20make%20the%20laws%20and%20policies%20for%20these%20fragile%20hills.%20So%20they%20can%20decide%20that%20certain%20industries%20are%20positive%20and%20others%20are%20not.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWithout%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%2C%20one%20entity%20will%20decide%20and%20it%20will%20not%20be%20in%20the%20best%20interests%20of%20the%20people.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20it%E2%80%99s%20about%20giving%20rights%20to%20the%20local%20indigenous%20people%20%E2%80%93%20because%20they%20will%20be%20concerned%20about%20the%20next%20generation%2C%20unlike%20a%20three-year%20term%20bureaucrat%2C%20Wangchuk%20said%2C%20in%20response%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20question%20about%20what%20will%20happen%20to%20the%20ecology%2C%20environment%20and%20the%20people%20of%20Ladakh%20if%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%20is%20not%20implemented.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELocal%2C%20indigenous%20people%20will%20be%20good%20stewards%20of%20the%20environment%20and%20take%20good%20care%20of%20it%2C%20as%20they%20always%20have%2C%20he%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20the%20virtual%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20same%20applies%20to%20the%20assembly%3A%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%20operates%20at%20the%20district%20or%20grassroots%20level%2C%20while%20statehood%20operates%20at%20the%20macro%2C%20state%20level%20because%20the%20funds%20for%20the%20state%20or%20the%20UT%20come%20from%20the%20Union%20government%20and%20right%20now%2C%20this%20is%20decided%20by%20just%20one%20lieutenant%20governor.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20from%20the%20region%20will%20never%20take%20decisions%20that%20come%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20next%20generation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThat%E2%80%99s%20why%20it%20is%20important%20for%20the%20environment%20that%20the%20sons%20and%20daughters%20of%20this%20soil%20be%20allowed%20to%20take%20decisions%20about%20this%20peculiar%20landscape%20and%20ecosystem%20that%20nobody%20else%20is%20likely%20to%20understand.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhy-citizens-groups-in-ladakh-are-turning-down-the-union-home-ministrys-olive-branch%5C%22%3EWhy%20Citizens%E2%80%99%20Groups%20in%20Ladakh%20Are%20Turning%20Down%20the%20Union%20Home%20Ministry%E2%80%99s%20Olive%20Branch%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Material%20development%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20excite%20us%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20two%20days%20ago%2C%20news%20reports%20talked%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Cclose%20collaboration%E2%80%9D%20being%20worked%20out%20between%20the%20governments%20of%20India%20and%20Iceland%20to%20explore%20more%20sources%20of%20geothermal%20energy%20in%20both%20Ladakh%20and%20Himachal%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGeothermal%20energy%20is%20energy%20obtained%20from%20hot%20water%20buried%20deep%20inside%20the%20earth%E2%80%99s%20surface%2C%20which%20can%20generate%20electricity%20from%20heat.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWells%20are%20being%20drilled%20as%20part%20of%20the%20endeavours%20to%20develop%20geothermal%20energy%20sources%2C%20Iceland%E2%80%99s%20foreign%20minister%20Bjarni%20Benediktsson%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aninews.in%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fasia%2Ficelands-foreign-minister-taps-geothermal-potential-in-ladakh-and-himachal-optimistic-on-direct-air-connectivity20240311183614%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etold%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20ANI%20on%20March%2011.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGeothermal%20energy%20is%20classified%20as%20a%20source%20of%20green%20energy%20because%20it%20is%20renewable%20and%20does%20not%20pollute%20the%20atmosphere%20as%20fossil%20fuels%20do.%20However%2C%20it%20comes%20with%20its%20own%20pitfalls%20in%20many%20cases.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20fact%2C%20a%20case%20in%20point%20exists%20in%20Ladakh%20itself.%20In%20Ladakh%E2%80%99s%20Puga%20Valley%2C%20India%20is%20building%20its%20first%20geothermal%20power%20plant%3B%20but%20the%20project%20is%20currently%20stalled%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F1059100%2Fin-ladakhs-puga-valley-geothermal-project-holds-promise-but-environmental-concerns-remain%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EScroll%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20because%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Ftopics%2Fengineering%2Fgeothermal-fluid%23definition%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Egeothermal%20fluid%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%93%20water%20containing%20dissolved%20minerals%20and%20sometimes%20even%20acids%20such%20as%20sulphuric%20and%20hydrochloric%20acid%20%E2%80%93%20leaked%20into%20the%20Puga%20stream%20in%20August%202022%2C%20and%20locals%20complained%20about%20the%20pollution.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20are%20these%20the%20kind%20of%20projects%20that%20Ladakhis%20would%20be%20able%20to%20regulate%20if%20they%20had%20the%20power%20to%20do%20so%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGeothermal%20and%20solar%20power%20plants%20are%20some%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmore%20benevolent%E2%80%9D%20projects%20being%20slated%20for%20Ladakh%20(though%20even%20some%20of%20these%20have%20problems)%2C%20Wangchuk%20replied%20in%20response%20to%20this%20question.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELadakhis%20would%20love%20to%20share%20their%20solar%20energy%20with%20the%20rest%20of%20India%2C%20but%20the%20location%20of%20such%20projects%20should%20be%20done%20in%20consultation%20with%20locals%2C%20he%20pointed%20out.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20instance%2C%20a%20ten%20gigawatt%20solar%20energy%20project%20is%20to%20come%20up%20in%20the%20Changthang%20region%20of%20Ladakh%2C%20per%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fchandigarh-news%2Fladakhs-mega-solar-power-project-delayed-to-be-ready-by-2026-101675761954786.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereports%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20However%2C%20this%20should%20have%20been%20decided%20with%20the%20consultation%20of%20the%20Changpa%20nomadic%20tribes%2C%20Wangchuk%20pointed%20out.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CCurrently%2C%20they%20are%20planning%20to%20take%20up%20roughly%20150%20square%20kilometres%20%E2%80%A6%20and%20this%20will%20be%20in%20prime%20pastures%20of%20these%20nomadic%20tribes%2C%20who%20produce%20some%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20finest%20pashmina%20%5Bwool%5D%20or%20cashmere%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20they%20%5Bthe%20Changpa%20tribes%5D%20were%20consulted%2C%20maybe%20they%20could%20have%20shown%20better%20places%20that%20do%20them%20less%20harm%2C%20or%20in%20other%20ways%20that%20benefit%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThen%20there%20is%20mining%2C%20of%20uranium%2C%20lithium%20and%20so%20on.%20Maybe%20locals%20can%20give%20solutions%20in%20which%20the%20mining%20can%20be%20conducted%20in%20a%20way%20that%20will%20not%20disable%20them%20for%20life%20for%20%E2%80%9Cso-called%20development%20which%20is%20not%20actually%20development%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20not%20so%20excited%20about%20material%20development%20where%20there%20is%20no%20limit%20to%20what%20you%20want%20and%20disregard%20every%20resource%20that%20nature%20has%2C%20disregard%20human%20indigenous%20populations%2C%20wildlife%2C%20flora%2C%20fauna.%20That%E2%80%99s%20not%20development.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHave%20people%20lost%20faith%20in%20the%20current%20government%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20the%20BJP%20not%20fulfilling%20its%20promises%20to%20Ladakh%20by%20not%20implementing%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%2C%20what%20does%20this%20mean%20for%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CMobilising%20peoples%E2%80%99%20movements%20is%20a%20basic%20part%20of%20a%20democracy%2C%E2%80%9D%20Wangchuk%20replied%20in%20response%20to%20this%20question%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20take%20guns%20or%20anything%2C%20we%20just%20want%20to%20make%20the%20government%20realise%20it%20%5Bour%20problem%5D%20by%20people%20inflicting%20pain%20on%20themselves%2C%20not%20on%20others.%20Not%20taking%20others%20hostage%2C%20but%20keeping%20myself%20hostage%20here%20for%2021%20days%2C%20hungry.%20So%20that%E2%80%99s%20what%20we%20will%20carry%20on.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20will%20be%20a%20critical%20mass%20of%20people%20that%20will%20be%20dangerous%20for%20the%20government%20after%20a%20point.%20It%20already%20exists%20in%20Ladakh%20%E2%80%A6%20any%20time%20a%20spark%20can%20blow%20it%20up.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CA%20government%20in%20a%20democracy%20is%20concerned%20about%20its%20votes%20and%20seats%20%E2%80%A6%20already%20in%20Ladakh%2C%20it%20is%20granted%20that%20they%20have%20lost%20the%20faith%20of%20the%20people%2C%20and%20therefore%20the%20votes%20and%20seat%5Bs%5D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20that%E2%80%99s%20not%20enough%2C%20one%20seat%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20matter.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20we%20are%20reaching%20out%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20India%20because%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20Ladakh%E2%80%99s%20issue%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20about%20what%20kind%20of%20democratic%20system%20we%20are%20going%20to%20have%E2%80%A6we%20want%20enough%20numbers%20of%20people%20to%20join%20us%20and%20this%20is%20the%20only%20way%20the%20government%20will%20move%20on%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20through%20your%20media%2C%20we%20want%20to%20appeal%20to%20the%20people%20of%20India%20that%20tomorrow%20it%20will%20be%20your%20turn.%20When%20it%20is%20happening%20in%20Ladakh%20we%20have%20to%20stand%20up%20for%20each%20other.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710352836000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13231912%2FWangchuk-Sonam.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fthis-is-about-truth-the-environment-and-democracy-says-sonam-wangchuk-on-day-8-of-his-climate-fast%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Wangchuk%20told%20%E2%80%98The%20Wire%E2%80%99%20that%20his%20climate%20fast%20is%20about%20giving%20rights%20to%20indigenous%20peoples%20in%20Ladakh%E2%80%99s%20administration%2C%20and%20that%20people%20have%20lost%20faith%20in%20the%20Union%20government.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fthis-is-about-truth-the-environment-and-democracy-says-sona