pecially%20one%20that%20is%20very%20laborious%20and%20customer-centric.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20worried%20if%20this%20hair%20oil%20would%20work%20on%20everyone.%20My%20idea%20was%20to%20help%20people%20manage%20hair%20fall.%20I%20never%20thought%20of%20doing%20a%20business%20and%20was%20unsure%20of%20facing%20everyting%20that%20it%20involved%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares%20candidly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20mother-in-law%20stood%20by%20her%20like%20a%20rock%20and%20defied%20her%20age%20to%20literally%20burn%20the%20midnight%20oil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20win%20for%20the%20duo%20was%20successfully%20fulfilling%20the%20100%20orders.%20From%20that%20day%20on%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20looking%20back.%20The%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334496%2Fkashmir-rukhsaar-sayeed-masterchef-india-chef-khalis-frozen-foods%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etwo-woman%20show%3C%2Fa%3E%20worked%20day%20and%20night%20to%20make%20the%20oil.%20Till%20September%202023%2C%20they%20made%20the%20oil%20at%20home%20and%20managed%20manufacturing%2C%20packaging%2C%20customer%20support%2C%20social%20media%2C%20and%20website%20all%20by%20themselves.%20After%20the%20success%20of%20their%20oil%2C%20they%20introduced%20a%20shampoo%20using%20Rajni%E2%80%99s%20recipe%2C%20a%20conditioner%2C%20scalp%20scrub%20and%20comb.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20they%20have%20over%208%2C000%20orders%20per%20month.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20the%20secret%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20938px)%20100vw%2C%20938px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fnidhi2-1709647312.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22938%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nidhi's%20Grandma%20Secret%20operates%20out%20of%20a%20manufacturing%20facility%20in%20Panchkula%5C%22%2